3
00:01:21,837 --> 00:01:24,298
"Ne možeš pobjeci od ljubavi."

4
00:01:25,090 --> 00:01:28,677
To je bio oglas
u Baltimorskim novinama.

5
00:01:29,761 --> 00:01:32,598
I tako ju je on našao.

6
00:01:33,932 --> 00:01:37,603
Ona je bila mlada žena
u potrazi za mužem.

7
00:01:38,061 --> 00:01:40,898
On je bio muškarac u potrazi
za suprugom.

8
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,878
Prekasno za govoriti mu razumno.

9
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,255
Ne možeš ju oženiti.
Nisi ju nikad sreo.

10
00:02:05,339 --> 00:02:09,343
Srest cu je danas. Brod iz Amerike
dolazi u 6:00, oženit cemo se u 9:00...

11
00:02:09,468 --> 00:02:11,011
...u 10:00, vratit cu se na posao.

12
00:02:11,428 --> 00:02:13,931
Smiješno. To je smiješno.

13
00:02:13,972 --> 00:02:18,519
Covjek treba ženu, nije li to ono
sto si mi govorio? Poslao sam po jednu.

14
00:02:18,602 --> 00:02:19,561
Iz Amerike.

15
00:02:19,645 --> 00:02:21,230
Kako ona izgleda?

16
00:02:22,814 --> 00:02:26,026
Doðe dan u životu svakog muškarca
kada band svira...

17
00:02:26,109 --> 00:02:30,531
...a on je jedini koji to cuje.
Danas je tvoj dan.

18
00:02:31,031 --> 00:02:32,699
Volim te.

19
00:02:33,450 --> 00:02:34,910
Ona nije prekrasna.

20
00:02:35,202 --> 00:02:37,371
Nije ni trebala biti prekrasna...

21
00:02:37,454 --> 00:02:40,666
...samo dobra, iskrena i dovoljno
mlada da rodi djecu.

22
00:02:41,792 --> 00:02:46,630
Hajde. Sunce ce uskoro izaci.
Brod ce doci.

23
00:02:48,632 --> 00:02:52,803
Ali što je s ljubavlju, Luis?
Zar ne bi tu negdje trebalo biti i ljubavi?

24
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:55,389
Ljubav nije za mene, Alan.

25
00:02:55,556 --> 00:02:57,766
Ljubav je za one ljude
koji vjeruju u nju.

26
00:02:59,268 --> 00:03:00,352
Idemo.

27
00:03:01,645 --> 00:03:04,940
Zašto mi se smiješ?
Smiješ mi se cijelo jutro.

28
00:03:04,982 --> 00:03:07,526
Nema veze. Idi! Hajde!

29
00:04:25,062 --> 00:04:27,898
Ne, ovo nije ljubavna prica.

30
00:04:28,565 --> 00:04:33,237
Ali je prica o ljubavi, i snazi
koju ima nad našim životom.

31
00:04:34,154 --> 00:04:37,032
Snazi da ozdravi ili uništi.

32
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:48,752
I ovdje prica pocinje.

33
00:05:05,227 --> 00:05:06,270
Mr. Vargas?

34
00:05:08,564 --> 00:05:10,023
Luis Vargas?

35
00:05:11,733 --> 00:05:13,694
Ne prepoznajete me, zar ne?

36
00:05:17,739 --> 00:05:19,157
Miss Russell?

37
00:05:20,409 --> 00:05:21,577
Da.

38
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,415
Julia Russell?

39
00:05:28,584 --> 00:05:30,252
Ali, ova slika--

40
00:05:30,294 --> 00:05:34,381
Prevarila sam vas.
Zao mi je. Nisam trebala.

41
00:05:35,257 --> 00:05:37,801
Bila sam nesigurna. Vidite...

42
00:05:38,427 --> 00:05:42,222
...nisam željela da se zainteresirate
za mene samo zbog moje ljepote.

43
00:05:43,765 --> 00:05:47,603
Zato sam poslala sliku neke
druge žene, a ne vlastitu.

44
00:05:50,272 --> 00:05:52,107
Vidim.

45
00:05:52,357 --> 00:05:56,028
Nadam se da cete mi oprostiti.
Mislila sam pisati puno puta. Probala sam.

46
00:05:56,278 --> 00:05:58,739
Ali hrabrost me je napustila. Pa sam....

47
00:06:05,537 --> 00:06:06,872
I....

48
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:14,713
Sad stojim pred vama kakva jesam,
i mislite sve najgore.

49
00:06:15,047 --> 00:06:16,215
Ne, ne.

50
00:06:17,382 --> 00:06:18,884
Nije baš tako loše.

51
00:06:20,552 --> 00:06:23,722
Samo, nije ono što sam oèekivao.

52
00:06:24,723 --> 00:06:27,893
Ako je moja prevara
promijenila vaše namjere...

53
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,728
...ako niste zadovoljni--

54
00:06:29,811 --> 00:06:31,063
Ne, nije to.

55
00:06:31,146 --> 00:06:34,399
...spremna sam se vratiti kuci
u Delaware.

56
00:06:34,525 --> 00:06:36,818
-Ako želite, vratit cu se.
-Miss Russell....

57
00:06:38,570 --> 00:06:39,905
Miss Russell...

58
00:06:43,575 --> 00:06:45,410
...bili ste iskreni sa mnom.

59
00:06:46,078 --> 00:06:48,413
I ja cu biti s vama.

60
00:06:50,374 --> 00:06:52,835
I ja cu priznati svoju prevaru.

61
00:06:56,713 --> 00:06:58,799
Ali vi izgledate isto kao
na slici.

62
00:06:58,924 --> 00:07:00,509
Da izgledam.

63
00:07:01,385 --> 00:07:04,012
Ali pisao sam vam da sam službenik...

64
00:07:04,096 --> 00:07:07,099
...u firmi za izvoz kave. Ali nisam.

65
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,728
Ja posjedujem firmu.

66
00:07:12,563 --> 00:07:14,189
To je moj biznis.

67
00:07:19,528 --> 00:07:22,114
Niste htjeli da se zainterisram
za vas...

68
00:07:22,197 --> 00:07:24,950
...samo zbog vašeg velikog
bankovnog racuna.

69
00:07:26,451 --> 00:07:27,494
da.

70
00:07:31,164 --> 00:07:33,333
Onda imamo nešto zajednickog.

71
00:07:34,751 --> 00:07:36,920
Ne može nam se vjerovati.

72
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:46,180
Naravno, ako je moja prevara
promijenila vaše namjere...

73
00:07:48,807 --> 00:07:52,477
...ako niste zainteresirani za
udaju za bogatog covjeka....

74
00:07:53,437 --> 00:07:55,689
Ne, mislim da je to u redu.

75
00:07:58,192 --> 00:08:01,111
Ako vama ne paše
nešto zgodnija žena.

76
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:05,574
Potrudit cu se.

77
00:08:20,923 --> 00:08:22,257
Miss Russell.

78
00:08:24,134 --> 00:08:25,469
Mr. Vargas.

79
00:08:26,970 --> 00:08:30,224
Sada imamo svo vrijeme
na svijetu da se upoznamo.

80
00:08:31,058 --> 00:08:32,976
Ne, ne svo vrijeme.

81
00:08:35,312 --> 00:08:37,731
Vjencat cemo se u 9:00.

82
00:08:39,650 --> 00:08:41,944
Onda bolje da požurimo.

83
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:55,290
"Uzmi ovaj prsten...

84
00:08:56,166 --> 00:08:58,001
"...kao znak moje ljubavi...

85
00:09:00,128 --> 00:09:01,547
"...i vjernosti...

86
00:09:01,964 --> 00:09:03,298
"...prema tebi."

87
00:09:27,823 --> 00:09:29,157
Muzika!

88
00:09:29,199 --> 00:09:30,534
Muzika!

89
00:09:39,710 --> 00:09:42,171
Dame i gospodo, zdravica!

90
00:09:43,172 --> 00:09:46,341
Našem mladoženji i njegovoj...

91
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:49,011
...ocaravajucoj mladoj!

92
00:09:54,099 --> 00:09:55,767
Želiš li plesati sa mnom?

93
00:09:56,059 --> 00:09:57,394
Ples?

94
00:09:59,396 --> 00:10:00,898
Ja ne plešem.

95
00:10:01,481 --> 00:10:03,233
Ja kažem da plešeš.

96
00:10:07,988 --> 00:10:12,409
Neka njihov život bude kao ples,
harmonican, lagan.

97
00:10:12,576 --> 00:10:15,412
Ples za citav zivot--

98
00:10:15,537 --> 00:10:17,372
Alan, previše je previše.

99
00:10:17,456 --> 00:10:18,749
Uskoro sam gotov.

100
00:10:18,832 --> 00:10:21,668
Sad si gotov. Sjedi.

101
00:11:12,010 --> 00:11:13,679
-Sve najbolje.
-Hvala.

102
00:11:46,086 --> 00:11:47,796
Da li želiš pogledati kucu?

103
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:50,716
Ne. Mogu je pogledati sutra.

104
00:11:54,678 --> 00:11:57,639
Daj mi par trenutaka.
Malo me je sram.

105
00:11:58,849 --> 00:12:03,437
Dat cu ti onoliko trenutaka,
dana, noci koliko trebaš.

106
00:12:05,856 --> 00:12:07,691
Kada želiš da doðem k tebi...

107
00:12:08,525 --> 00:12:09,860
...doci cu.

108
00:12:11,069 --> 00:12:12,404
Ne prije.

109
00:12:17,826 --> 00:12:19,286
Ucinit ces to za mene?

110
00:12:21,330 --> 00:12:22,998
Ako želiš, budem.

111
00:12:30,088 --> 00:12:31,423
Onda...

112
00:12:32,174 --> 00:12:34,009
...laku noc.

113
00:12:39,223 --> 00:12:41,225
Soba je tamo, desno.

114
00:12:42,184 --> 00:12:44,144
Mislim da cu je naci.

115
00:13:57,259 --> 00:13:59,094
Konacno si budan.

116
00:14:01,138 --> 00:14:02,764
Dan je vec napola prošao.

117
00:14:05,601 --> 00:14:07,436
Oprosti. Nisam obucen.

118
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:10,314
Mogu sacekati vani,
ali kava ce se ohladiti.

119
00:14:10,647 --> 00:14:12,107
Ne, u redu je.

120
00:14:12,608 --> 00:14:16,069
Ako mi neko bude nosio kavu
svako jutro prije nego što se obucem...

121
00:14:16,195 --> 00:14:18,238
...bit cu jako sretna.

122
00:14:18,822 --> 00:14:20,282
To ce promijeniti dan.

123
00:14:20,407 --> 00:14:21,491
Ali...

124
00:14:22,201 --> 00:14:24,161
...Ti piješ samo caj.

125
00:14:24,244 --> 00:14:25,913
Da? Ne.

126
00:14:26,663 --> 00:14:30,501
Kad sam pisao da radi u firmi za
proizvodnju kave ti si napisala--

127
00:14:30,584 --> 00:14:32,252
To je bila moja sestra.

128
00:14:33,045 --> 00:14:37,591
Vjerovala je da je kava grešno zadovoljstvo
pa sam se pretvarala da se slažem.

129
00:14:37,674 --> 00:14:41,887
Citala je sva moja pisma tebi,
pa nisam uvijek mogla biti iskrena.

130
00:14:45,641 --> 00:14:49,603
Još jedan razlog da ih zaboraviš.
To je sve sad iza tebe.

131
00:14:51,772 --> 00:14:53,482
Sto misliš?

132
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:56,610
O cemu?

133
00:14:59,696 --> 00:15:01,990
Da li misliš kao i moja sestra...

134
00:15:02,699 --> 00:15:06,036
...da je uživanje uvijek grešno?

135
00:16:04,469 --> 00:16:06,972
Zašto si izabrao ženu iz Amerike?

136
00:16:09,099 --> 00:16:11,351
Mi smo ovdje prošlost.

137
00:16:12,936 --> 00:16:14,730
Vi ste tamo buducnost.

138
00:16:17,191 --> 00:16:20,277
Zašto si odabrala odlazak?

139
00:16:21,278 --> 00:16:23,447
Da pobjegnem od buducnosti.

140
00:16:25,324 --> 00:16:27,826
Da postanem netko drugi.

141
00:16:30,996 --> 00:16:33,832
Netko sam drugi s tobom.

142
00:16:36,210 --> 00:16:37,878
Netko više kao...

143
00:16:38,712 --> 00:16:40,047
...ja.

144
00:16:58,315 --> 00:17:00,484
Tamo, u njegovom zagrljaju...

145
00:17:00,943 --> 00:17:02,903
...postala je netko drugi.

146
00:17:04,696 --> 00:17:06,698
Netko, netko kao ona sama.

147
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:22,587
Kažem ti, nikad nisam bio sretniji.

148
00:19:23,296 --> 00:19:25,757
Ne postoji "sretno oženjen".

149
00:19:25,841 --> 00:19:28,677
To je nelogicno, kao "sretno mrtav".

150
00:19:30,262 --> 00:19:33,849
Mislio sam da ces se do sada
vec vratiti kurvama.

151
00:19:33,932 --> 00:19:35,767
Ici malo svojim kreolkama.

152
00:19:35,809 --> 00:19:36,935
Ne više.

153
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:39,396
Imao si ju za sebe
vec dovoljno dugo.

154
00:19:39,479 --> 00:19:41,314
Kad cemo ju ponovno vidjeti?

155
00:19:41,398 --> 00:19:43,316
Idemo u kazalište slijedeci tjedan.

156
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,569
Americki zabavljaci koje
želi vidjeti.

157
00:19:45,652 --> 00:19:46,903
Pridruži nam se.

158
00:19:54,786 --> 00:19:58,749
Soon comes the morning
when the knell is rung...

159
00:19:59,124 --> 00:20:01,293
...to take my living breath.

160
00:20:01,376 --> 00:20:03,628
Come, come, the night is almost done.

161
00:20:08,341 --> 00:20:09,968
Satan is near!

162
00:20:10,802 --> 00:20:12,721
The shrieking, grim and...

163
00:20:12,804 --> 00:20:16,058
...hideous brim of hell to uncover.

164
00:20:16,308 --> 00:20:19,144
Come, or you will share her wretched end.

165
00:20:19,478 --> 00:20:22,147
Hellhound! Abominable monster!

166
00:20:22,481 --> 00:20:24,649
Would that I had never been born!

167
00:20:29,488 --> 00:20:31,156
Prekrasno.

168
00:20:31,490 --> 00:20:32,824
Odvratno.

169
00:20:33,492 --> 00:20:34,951
Jeftina melodrama.

170
00:20:36,578 --> 00:20:41,249
Was it we who forced our way to you?
Who was it sent her to her ruin?

171
00:20:41,583 --> 00:20:42,918
I...

172
00:20:44,169 --> 00:20:45,504
...or you?

173
00:20:46,338 --> 00:20:49,800
What evil thing has risen from the ground?

174
00:20:50,342 --> 00:20:54,304
Father, let angels now have charge of me...

175
00:20:54,554 --> 00:20:57,391
...encamped around heavenly company.

176
00:20:57,766 --> 00:20:59,559
She is condemned to die.

177
00:21:01,019 --> 00:21:03,605
She is redeemed on high!

178
00:21:03,855 --> 00:21:05,690
Hither, to me!

179
00:21:16,868 --> 00:21:20,038
Julia, draga, izgledas rumeno.

180
00:21:20,622 --> 00:21:23,625
-Jesi dobro?
-Da, to je od kazališta.

181
00:21:23,917 --> 00:21:25,252
Obožavam ga...

182
00:21:25,544 --> 00:21:27,212
...cak i jeftine melodrame.

183
00:21:30,048 --> 00:21:31,216
Oprostite.

184
00:21:37,723 --> 00:21:39,808
Da li pati od groznica?

185
00:21:40,434 --> 00:21:43,061
Pati od malo previše ruža.

186
00:21:43,311 --> 00:21:46,815
Glupost. Dama ne stavlja ruž.

187
00:21:47,149 --> 00:21:48,817
Ne, dama ne.

188
00:21:49,151 --> 00:21:52,821
I dama ne luta sama po
kazalištu.

189
00:21:54,823 --> 00:21:56,158
Oprostite.

190
00:22:00,787 --> 00:22:03,915
Možda ce vam drugi cin
biti bolji.

191
00:22:57,844 --> 00:23:00,889
Oprostite, gospodine!
Publici nije dozvoljeno iza pozornice.

192
00:23:00,972 --> 00:23:02,933
Ne dirajte me.

193
00:23:03,016 --> 00:23:04,935
Dovraga, to je moja žena!

194
00:23:05,018 --> 00:23:07,145
Luis, došao si me spasiti...

195
00:23:08,105 --> 00:23:09,439
...kao u predstavi....

196
00:23:11,441 --> 00:23:13,276
Što radiš ovdje?

197
00:23:13,443 --> 00:23:17,406
Nije li uzbudljivo?
Pogledaj ove cudne naprave.

198
00:23:17,614 --> 00:23:21,326
-Tko je bio taj covjek?
-Koji covjek? Izgubila sam se, to je sve.

199
00:23:21,868 --> 00:23:23,537
Stalo mi je srce zbog tebe.

200
00:23:23,704 --> 00:23:26,665
Osjeti. Osjecaš kako udara?

201
00:23:31,628 --> 00:23:32,629
Isuse.

202
00:23:33,422 --> 00:23:35,173
Umrijet cu zbog tebe.

203
00:23:38,802 --> 00:23:40,470
Nadam se.

204
00:23:44,182 --> 00:23:45,642
Na mjesta, molim.

205
00:23:45,809 --> 00:23:48,311
Dame i gospodo, drugi cin.

206
00:23:56,570 --> 00:23:58,196
Odvedi me kuci.

207
00:24:08,874 --> 00:24:11,043
Draga sestro.

208
00:24:11,168 --> 00:24:16,381
Ne znam zašto si takva sa mnom.
Prošlo je puno tjedana kako si otišla.

209
00:24:16,965 --> 00:24:21,094
Za sve to vrijeme ni rijeci, da me
obavijestiš o svom sigurnom dolasku...

210
00:24:21,344 --> 00:24:25,348
...da li si srela Mr. Vargasa,
da li je bilo svadbe.

211
00:24:25,682 --> 00:24:27,392
Što da mislim?

212
00:24:27,934 --> 00:24:30,687
Kontaktirala sam ambasadu u Havani...

213
00:24:30,896 --> 00:24:33,231
...i vlasti tamo u  Santiagu.

214
00:24:33,315 --> 00:24:36,109
Znam što osjecaš prema njoj, ali...

215
00:24:36,777 --> 00:24:38,153
...moraš joj pisati.

216
00:24:40,614 --> 00:24:43,283
Moraš, prije nego
nam pošalje policiju.

217
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:46,036
U pravu si.
Nisam bila dobra prema njoj.

218
00:24:46,495 --> 00:24:49,664
Iako ona nikad nije bila
dobra prema meni.

219
00:24:51,583 --> 00:24:53,585
Samo napravi to.

220
00:24:55,128 --> 00:24:57,422
Napravi to, i onda je gotovo.

221
00:24:57,464 --> 00:24:59,466
Ne, ne, ne!

222
00:25:01,802 --> 00:25:05,138
U redu je. Ja sam, Luis.

223
00:25:06,348 --> 00:25:07,682
Sanjala si.

224
00:25:09,643 --> 00:25:10,936
Jesi u redu?

225
00:25:15,315 --> 00:25:17,651
To je to.

226
00:25:17,984 --> 00:25:20,654
Samo si sanjala.

227
00:25:23,490 --> 00:25:24,825
U redu je.

228
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:28,453
To je bio samo san.

229
00:25:28,829 --> 00:25:32,082
Ružan san, to je sve.

230
00:25:40,465 --> 00:25:41,633
Bio je samo san.

231
00:25:42,008 --> 00:25:44,219
Jesi OK? Trebaš li nešto?

232
00:25:44,302 --> 00:25:45,262
Tebe.

233
00:25:46,096 --> 00:25:47,431
Zao mi je.

234
00:25:47,764 --> 00:25:49,933
Sad si sa mnom. Sigurna.

235
00:25:50,183 --> 00:25:51,977
Sve je u redu.

236
00:25:52,436 --> 00:25:53,937
Hoces li ostati?

237
00:25:54,146 --> 00:25:55,480
Naravno.

238
00:25:56,690 --> 00:25:57,983
Naravno.

239
00:25:59,818 --> 00:26:01,486
Sve je u redu.

240
00:26:32,934 --> 00:26:35,103
Luis, nemoj ici.

241
00:26:37,439 --> 00:26:40,108
Kako je ovo jutro
kraljica kuce?

242
00:26:44,863 --> 00:26:47,532
Pogledaj. Vidiš? Napisala sam.

243
00:26:49,409 --> 00:26:52,037
Tako je najbolje. Hvala ti.

244
00:26:52,287 --> 00:26:56,083
-Reci cu Sari da pošalje.
-Nema potrebe. Mogu i sam.

245
00:26:56,166 --> 00:26:58,168
Nisam adresirala.

246
00:26:58,251 --> 00:27:02,214
Imam adresu u uredu.
Onda je na putu.

247
00:27:10,931 --> 00:27:12,724
Što ces danas raditi?

248
00:27:12,808 --> 00:27:16,144
Idem Engleskom krojacu
na Plaza Vieja.

249
00:27:19,231 --> 00:27:20,399
Trebat ces novaca.

250
00:27:22,150 --> 00:27:24,861
Potpisite ovdje, Senora.

251
00:27:26,488 --> 00:27:29,783
Da li je to i za osobni i za
poslovni racun?

252
00:27:29,866 --> 00:27:31,410
Da, hvala.

253
00:27:31,785 --> 00:27:34,788
Želim da mi žena ima pravo
korištenja svih racuna.

254
00:27:35,205 --> 00:27:36,248
Evo ga.

255
00:27:36,331 --> 00:27:38,583
Da li da potpišem s
djevojackim imenom?

256
00:27:39,042 --> 00:27:40,502
Ne, s vjencanim.

257
00:27:40,794 --> 00:27:44,214
Morate zapamtiti da ponovite
potpis uvijek isto...

258
00:27:44,548 --> 00:27:46,383
...svaki put kad podižete cek.

259
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:48,427
Pokušat cu.

260
00:27:59,312 --> 00:28:00,939
O, covjece!

261
00:28:09,948 --> 00:28:12,284
Pa, Luis, da li je to
konacno ljubav...

262
00:28:12,534 --> 00:28:14,494
...ili samo strast?

263
00:28:15,579 --> 00:28:16,955
Ima li razlike?

264
00:28:17,289 --> 00:28:18,457
Ima, ima.

265
00:28:18,665 --> 00:28:22,294
Voljeti nekoga je davanje,
i onda željeti dati još više.

266
00:28:22,961 --> 00:28:24,463
A strast?

267
00:28:24,963 --> 00:28:26,256
Što je strast, Alane?

268
00:28:27,049 --> 00:28:30,218
Strast je uzimanje, i onda
uzimati još više.

269
00:28:30,510 --> 00:28:33,305
Progutati, konzumirati.
Bez logike, bez razuma.

270
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:36,516
Pa...uzimanje, davanje.

271
00:28:37,350 --> 00:28:38,685
Koje je?

272
00:28:39,186 --> 00:28:40,479
Oboje.

273
00:28:43,482 --> 00:28:45,442
Želim joj dati sve.

274
00:28:47,069 --> 00:28:49,321
I onda joj želim sve uzeti.

275
00:28:50,572 --> 00:28:53,825
O, Luis. Ti si izgubljen.

276
00:28:54,409 --> 00:28:55,744
Ne, ne.

277
00:28:57,788 --> 00:28:59,998
Ona je ta koja je izgubljena.

278
00:29:00,624 --> 00:29:04,294
Kako, zašto, ne znam.
Ali to ce se promijeniti.

279
00:29:05,545 --> 00:29:07,339
Ja mogu to promijeniti.

280
00:29:14,262 --> 00:29:15,347
Mr. Vargas?

281
00:29:17,808 --> 00:29:20,060
Walter Downs.
Nisam vas mislio preplašiti.

282
00:29:20,394 --> 00:29:22,979
-U redu je.
-Receno mi je da vas mogu tu naci.

283
00:29:23,063 --> 00:29:24,564
-Kako vam mogu pomoci?
-Ništa važno.

284
00:29:24,648 --> 00:29:27,567
Skoro nevažno.
Zarucio sam se za Miss Russell.

285
00:29:27,651 --> 00:29:28,777
Mislite Juliju?

286
00:29:29,111 --> 00:29:31,446
Ne, Emily. Njezinu sestru.

287
00:29:31,738 --> 00:29:32,864
U Delawareu.

288
00:29:32,906 --> 00:29:34,783
Ja sam privatni istražitelj.

289
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:37,077
Tek sam stigao iz Wilmingtona.

290
00:29:37,577 --> 00:29:42,207
Razumijem.
Znam da je Miss Russell zabrinuta.

291
00:29:42,249 --> 00:29:45,252
Ali pisali smo joj prije
nekoliko tjedana.

292
00:29:45,627 --> 00:29:50,132
Siguran sam da ce osjetiti veliko
olakšanje kad dobije to pismo.

293
00:29:50,215 --> 00:29:52,217
Znaci Miss Julia je dobro?

294
00:29:52,592 --> 00:29:55,721
Više nego dobro.
I više nije Miss Julia.

295
00:29:56,138 --> 00:29:57,848
Ona je Senora Vargas, moja žena.

296
00:29:57,931 --> 00:29:59,391
Znaci vi ste oženjeni?

297
00:30:02,144 --> 00:30:04,271
-To su odlicne vijesti.
-Sretno oženjeni.

298
00:30:04,354 --> 00:30:05,897
To vidim.

299
00:30:06,022 --> 00:30:09,192
Kakva misterija je sretan brak.

300
00:30:09,776 --> 00:30:12,237
Rumenilo na obrazu,
Sjaj u oku.

301
00:30:13,113 --> 00:30:15,449
-Mislim da se to vidi.
-Vidi se, svakako.

302
00:30:15,532 --> 00:30:17,743
Miss Russell ce biti
sretna da to cuje.

303
00:30:18,326 --> 00:30:20,287
Bilo bi mi drago kad bi
joj to rekli.

304
00:30:20,370 --> 00:30:21,663
Svakako cu joj to reci.

305
00:30:23,373 --> 00:30:27,044
I bit cu još više uvjeren
kad sretnem vašu ženu.

306
00:30:30,505 --> 00:30:31,673
Da, da.

307
00:30:32,549 --> 00:30:33,467
Zašto da ne?

308
00:30:36,636 --> 00:30:38,722
Bit cemo doma u nedjelju popodne.

309
00:30:39,473 --> 00:30:41,308
Želite li doci na kavu?

310
00:30:41,683 --> 00:30:42,684
Da, doci cu.

311
00:30:42,768 --> 00:30:46,146
Porucite vašoj ženi kako se
veselim što cu ju upoznati.

312
00:30:57,908 --> 00:31:00,077
Vani molim. Na terasi.

313
00:31:01,328 --> 00:31:02,662
Napravite kako kaže.

314
00:31:06,166 --> 00:31:07,959
Baš na vrijeme.

315
00:31:08,794 --> 00:31:11,963
Ovo je za nedjelju,
a ovo za preko tjedna.

316
00:31:12,547 --> 00:31:14,549
Dobro, dobro.

317
00:31:15,717 --> 00:31:17,302
A ostalo?

318
00:31:17,511 --> 00:31:19,388
Ovo mi se sviða.

319
00:31:20,180 --> 00:31:23,058
Što misliš?
Ima sedam dana u tjednu.

320
00:31:24,184 --> 00:31:26,186
Zar nema ništa u tvom sanduku?

321
00:31:26,269 --> 00:31:30,023
Ništa dobro.
A, i izgubila sam kljuc.

322
00:31:30,107 --> 00:31:33,693
Pozvat cemo bravara.
Ma to je lako. Zapravo...

323
00:31:33,944 --> 00:31:35,821
...sam cu to napraviti.

324
00:31:37,239 --> 00:31:40,075
Ne, želim ti nešto pokazati. Doði.

325
00:31:41,368 --> 00:31:44,037
Morate sada otici.
Poljubit cu svog muža.

326
00:31:44,162 --> 00:31:46,623
Onda cemo se okupati.

327
00:32:03,724 --> 00:32:05,350
Što to osjecam?

328
00:32:06,059 --> 00:32:07,477
Moj parfem.

329
00:32:07,769 --> 00:32:08,937
Ne.

330
00:32:10,856 --> 00:32:12,190
Cigaru.

331
00:32:13,817 --> 00:32:15,318
Probala sam jednu.

332
00:32:17,612 --> 00:32:19,114
Jednu moju cigaru?

333
00:32:19,906 --> 00:32:22,242
Željela sam tvoj okus u
mojim ustima.

334
00:32:26,121 --> 00:32:28,123
Nemaš nikavog srama.

335
00:32:29,249 --> 00:32:31,543
Nema ništa sramno ako
se volimo.

336
00:32:32,294 --> 00:32:34,296
Voliš li me? Julia?

337
00:32:34,963 --> 00:32:36,631
Voliš li me?

338
00:32:37,549 --> 00:32:39,760
Ili nisi tip koji voli?

339
00:33:19,841 --> 00:33:21,676
Zaboravio sam ti reci.

340
00:33:23,512 --> 00:33:26,014
Dolazi nam gost u nedjelju.

341
00:33:27,307 --> 00:33:28,683
Da?

342
00:33:29,726 --> 00:33:30,977
Da...

343
00:33:31,144 --> 00:33:33,271
...pravi privatni istražitelj...

344
00:33:34,898 --> 00:33:37,067
...cak iz Delawarea.

345
00:33:38,652 --> 00:33:40,987
Emily ga je poslala.

346
00:33:41,279 --> 00:33:44,032
Da. Detektiv Downs.

347
00:33:44,324 --> 00:33:46,493
Rekao si Detektiv Downs?

348
00:33:46,618 --> 00:33:49,413
Ne brini, samo želi
vidjeti da si dobro...

349
00:33:50,122 --> 00:33:52,791
...i sretna i stvarno moja supruga.

350
00:33:53,875 --> 00:33:58,213
-I onda je ova glupost gotova.
-Kad ce ta ptica prestati kreštati?

351
00:34:00,340 --> 00:34:01,508
Julia.

352
00:34:07,597 --> 00:34:10,267
Pazi, stiže.

353
00:34:24,573 --> 00:34:26,241
O, ne.

354
00:34:30,954 --> 00:34:33,999
Don Luis, pogledajte. Mrtav je.

355
00:34:35,375 --> 00:34:36,835
Samo je pjevao.

356
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:39,296
Sad ne pjeva, zar ne?

357
00:34:40,547 --> 00:34:43,341
Izgleda kao da mu je slomljen
njegov mali vrat.

358
00:34:44,384 --> 00:34:48,180
Odnesite ga.
Ne želim da ga Julija vidi.

359
00:35:41,108 --> 00:35:43,527
Kako je osoba umrla na
ovom instrumentu?

360
00:35:46,113 --> 00:35:47,906
Mislim da...

361
00:35:49,699 --> 00:35:52,577
...mu je okretanje tocka
slomilo vrat.

362
00:35:53,745 --> 00:35:55,414
A ako nije?

363
00:35:56,456 --> 00:35:58,291
Da li se onda udavi?

364
00:36:00,335 --> 00:36:01,586
Da li se bojiš?

365
00:36:05,090 --> 00:36:06,049
Ne.

366
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:08,802
Julia se ne boji.

367
00:36:10,804 --> 00:36:12,264
Ali Bonny da.

368
00:36:13,974 --> 00:36:17,936
Ne razumijem. Tko je Bonny?

369
00:36:22,941 --> 00:36:24,401
Tko je Bonny?

370
00:36:26,778 --> 00:36:28,447
Tražim Mr. Vargasa.

371
00:36:28,572 --> 00:36:30,866
To je pitanje koje
ce Luis uskoro pitati.

372
00:36:36,872 --> 00:36:38,206
Mr. Vargas?

373
00:36:39,166 --> 00:36:40,459
Moje ime je Russell.

374
00:36:41,334 --> 00:36:42,753
Emily Russell.

375
00:36:43,045 --> 00:36:44,880
Ja sam Julijina sestra.

376
00:36:46,339 --> 00:36:51,303
Pa razumijete kako sam se
uznemirila primajuci ovo pismo.

377
00:36:51,762 --> 00:36:52,929
Uznemirila?

378
00:36:53,221 --> 00:36:57,392
Ali...mislio sam da ce
vam biti drago kad ga primite.

379
00:36:58,894 --> 00:37:00,729
Ovo pismo, gospodine...

380
00:37:01,396 --> 00:37:04,566
...pisano da odgovori na
ono koje sam ja poslala...

381
00:37:04,900 --> 00:37:07,235
...i potpisano njezinim
imenom...

382
00:37:07,736 --> 00:37:09,738
...nije od Julie.

383
00:37:11,865 --> 00:37:13,950
Naravno da je.

384
00:37:14,576 --> 00:37:15,786
Ja sam ga poslao.

385
00:37:15,911 --> 00:37:17,954
Nije pisano od moje sestre.

386
00:37:18,038 --> 00:37:19,456
Miss Russell.

387
00:37:24,753 --> 00:37:27,255
Žao mi je.

388
00:37:27,422 --> 00:37:30,300
Nemojte biti uznemireni.
Kunem vam se--

389
00:37:30,384 --> 00:37:32,511
Kunite se koliko želite.

390
00:37:36,223 --> 00:37:39,684
To nije Julijin rukopis.

391
00:37:40,227 --> 00:37:42,604
To je rukopis stranca.

392
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:45,023
Nepoznate osobe.

393
00:37:46,066 --> 00:37:47,526
Meni nepoznate.

394
00:38:16,638 --> 00:38:19,474
-Gdje je ona?
-Mislio sam poslati po vas.

395
00:38:19,558 --> 00:38:20,892
Gdje je ona?

396
00:38:21,935 --> 00:38:23,729
Odlazi. Izlazi!

397
00:38:34,823 --> 00:38:35,991
Gdje je otišla?

398
00:38:36,074 --> 00:38:40,037
Ne znam. Poslala me je
u poštu.Kad sam se vratio--

399
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:23,288
Nece se vratiti, zar ne, Sara?

400
00:39:23,538 --> 00:39:24,998
Nikad ni nije bila ovdje.

401
00:39:27,125 --> 00:39:29,086
Bili ste oženjeni za san.

402
00:39:30,087 --> 00:39:32,339
San koji vam je ukrao dušu.

403
00:39:58,073 --> 00:40:00,409
Luis! Što je?

404
00:40:05,664 --> 00:40:10,419
Vaša žena se pojavila pet
minuta prije zatvaranja.

405
00:40:10,752 --> 00:40:15,090
Kako ste željeli, dao sam joj
pun pristup na vaše racune.

406
00:40:16,174 --> 00:40:18,218
Vaše stanje na zatvaranju bilo je...

407
00:40:18,719 --> 00:40:21,847
...51 dolar i 40 centa
na jednom racunu...

408
00:40:22,055 --> 00:40:23,849
...10 dolara na drugom.

409
00:40:29,396 --> 00:40:32,691
Kako sam objasnio vašoj ženi,
zatvoriti oba racuna totalno...

410
00:40:32,733 --> 00:40:35,402
...trebao bi vaš potpis.

411
00:40:41,074 --> 00:40:42,409
Žao mi je.

412
00:41:11,772 --> 00:41:13,065
Don Luis?

413
00:41:45,097 --> 00:41:47,432
Mora da je bog bio
ljut na tebe taj dan...

414
00:41:47,933 --> 00:41:50,894
...kad ti je dopustio da pogledaš
lice te žene.

415
00:42:04,366 --> 00:42:07,035
Želim je nazad. Sara...

416
00:42:09,621 --> 00:42:11,289
...želim je nazad.

417
00:42:14,209 --> 00:42:17,754
Ne, carino. Zašto?

418
00:42:19,339 --> 00:42:21,842
Zašto ju ponovno želiš nazad?

419
00:43:57,711 --> 00:43:59,838
Ne, ovo nije ljubavna prica.

420
00:44:01,715 --> 00:44:03,842
Ovo je prica o ljubavi.

421
00:44:06,386 --> 00:44:10,098
O onima koji su joj se prepustili,
i cijeni koju su platili.

422
00:44:13,643 --> 00:44:16,855
i o onima koji su pobjegli od
nje zato jer su se preplašili...

423
00:44:18,440 --> 00:44:21,777
...ili zato što nisu vjerovali.
da se ona isplati

424
00:44:24,488 --> 00:44:26,156
Ona je pobjegla.

425
00:44:27,157 --> 00:44:28,492
On je odustao.

426
00:44:28,909 --> 00:44:30,202
Mr. Vargas?

427
00:44:32,204 --> 00:44:33,872
Walter Downs.

428
00:44:37,125 --> 00:44:39,211
Koja sretna slucajnost.

429
00:44:40,337 --> 00:44:41,671
O, da.

430
00:44:43,215 --> 00:44:44,883
Sjecam vas se.

431
00:44:50,764 --> 00:44:54,434
I vlasti ovdje nisu mogle
ništa napraviti?

432
00:44:57,604 --> 00:44:59,272
Nakon svega...

433
00:45:01,108 --> 00:45:02,776
...nije bilo zlocina.

434
00:45:04,152 --> 00:45:08,990
Bila je moja žena. Samo je uzela
ono što sam joj dao

435
00:45:11,743 --> 00:45:13,078
Vaš novac.

436
00:45:15,122 --> 00:45:16,581
I vašu ljubav.

437
00:45:19,376 --> 00:45:21,086
I niste ništa posumnjali?

438
00:45:26,258 --> 00:45:31,096
Cini mi se da znam puno manje
o ženama nego što sam mislio.

439
00:45:32,097 --> 00:45:33,348
A ja znam previše.

440
00:45:33,765 --> 00:45:36,226
Nemam baš neke koristi od njih...

441
00:45:36,601 --> 00:45:38,562
...osim onog najpotrebnijeg.

442
00:45:39,020 --> 00:45:42,190
Za pravo druženje,
preferiram muško društvo.

443
00:45:43,567 --> 00:45:44,901
Slušajte me.

444
00:45:46,737 --> 00:45:48,405
Možete li je naci?

445
00:45:52,284 --> 00:45:53,618
Možda.

446
00:45:55,454 --> 00:45:58,290
Ali, trenutno sam...

447
00:45:58,373 --> 00:46:02,377
...zauzet u pronalaženju prave
Julije, one koju ste trebali oženiti.

448
00:46:04,963 --> 00:46:06,631
Jeste li ju našli?

449
00:46:07,799 --> 00:46:09,760
Jeste li ju našli?

450
00:46:11,970 --> 00:46:13,263
Još ne.

451
00:46:13,346 --> 00:46:15,515
Ako budete...

452
00:46:15,807 --> 00:46:19,144
...možda vas odvede do Julije
koju sam ja oženio.

453
00:46:20,562 --> 00:46:21,855
Možda.

454
00:46:23,023 --> 00:46:24,316
I obrnuto.

455
00:46:27,194 --> 00:46:31,490
Platit cu vam koliko god treba,
ako ju možete naci za mene.

456
00:46:32,074 --> 00:46:33,909
To je sve što želim.

457
00:46:34,534 --> 00:46:37,496
Onda pretpostavljam da ste
nadoknadili vaše gubitke.

458
00:46:38,538 --> 00:46:41,375
Rekao sam da cu platiti
koliko god želite.

459
00:46:41,750 --> 00:46:43,085
Platit cu.

460
00:46:43,251 --> 00:46:45,587
Da, vjerujem da budete.

461
00:46:46,421 --> 00:46:48,423
A ako naðem vašu Juliju?

462
00:46:48,757 --> 00:46:51,218
Aka vam ju dovedem...

463
00:46:52,052 --> 00:46:53,804
...ili dovedem vas do nje...

464
00:46:55,222 --> 00:46:57,849
...što ce vam to
dobroga donijeti?

465
00:46:58,558 --> 00:46:59,643
Novac je otišao.

466
00:47:01,561 --> 00:47:02,854
Ljubav...

467
00:47:03,647 --> 00:47:04,940
...uništena.

468
00:47:06,358 --> 00:47:08,568
Što bi još mogli
htjeti od nje?

469
00:47:10,695 --> 00:47:12,531
Što bi još mogli željeti?

470
00:47:18,870 --> 00:47:20,539
Želim je ubiti.

471
00:47:42,185 --> 00:47:44,646
Da, sjecam se te dame.

472
00:47:45,105 --> 00:47:47,399
Mršava, tamna i jako....

473
00:47:48,275 --> 00:47:52,446
Sjecam se kad je dolazila niz palubu
i povjetarac joj je uhvatio suknju.

474
00:47:52,904 --> 00:47:54,406
Dolazila je prema meni.

475
00:47:54,614 --> 00:47:59,286
Brzo ju je uhvatila i
onda mi se osmjehnula.

476
00:48:00,203 --> 00:48:03,540
Mislim da je putovala s
grupom Americkih glumaca...

477
00:48:03,623 --> 00:48:04,791
...na turneji po otoku.

478
00:48:05,083 --> 00:48:07,252
O da, sjecam se.

479
00:48:07,627 --> 00:48:10,714
Zamotala je malo salate
u njezinu salvetu.

480
00:48:11,465 --> 00:48:15,510
To mi je bilo cudno. Objasnila
mi je da je to za njenu pticu.

481
00:48:15,761 --> 00:48:17,763
Putovala je s pticom.

482
00:48:18,305 --> 00:48:21,224
O da, sjecam je se.

483
00:48:21,641 --> 00:48:24,102
Dama s krletkom...

484
00:48:25,020 --> 00:48:27,064
...ali ovo ne lici na nju.

485
00:48:27,647 --> 00:48:29,941
Bila je mlada i jako zgodna.

486
00:48:31,485 --> 00:48:33,028
Da, to je ona.

487
00:48:34,780 --> 00:48:37,532
A prava Julija se nije pojavila zato...

488
00:48:38,241 --> 00:48:39,409
...što je mrtva.

489
00:48:42,954 --> 00:48:44,956
-Mislite ubijena.
-Da.

490
00:48:46,541 --> 00:48:48,752
Možda je imala suucesnika.

491
00:48:48,960 --> 00:48:51,171
Takve žene cesto imaju suucesnika.

492
00:48:51,421 --> 00:48:54,174
Nekoga koga može iskoristiti
i onda odbaciti.

493
00:48:54,674 --> 00:48:58,970
Nekoga ko je možda u potrazi za
njom isto kao i nas dvojica.

494
00:49:01,181 --> 00:49:02,766
Ovdje se to dogodilo.

495
00:49:03,433 --> 00:49:05,435
Ovdje u Havani.

496
00:50:05,996 --> 00:50:08,331
Ovuda gospodo. Dobrodošli u Havanu.

497
00:50:08,707 --> 00:50:11,168
Mr. Downs ce biti u sobi 37...

498
00:50:11,209 --> 00:50:14,880
...a Mr. Vargas ce biti niz hodnik
u sobi 42.

499
00:50:17,174 --> 00:50:20,510
Povezat cu se s
lokalnim vlastima...

500
00:50:21,261 --> 00:50:24,264
...i pogledati da li se nedavno
pojavio kakav mrtvac.

501
00:50:24,723 --> 00:50:26,475
Možete mi se pridružiti.

502
00:50:28,727 --> 00:50:30,645
Ne, hvala.

503
00:50:31,646 --> 00:50:35,942
Havana je jako lijep grad,
pogotovo za vrijeme karnevala.

504
00:50:36,359 --> 00:50:40,697
Predlažem restoran "Opera".
Preko puta ulice je.

505
00:50:42,866 --> 00:50:45,369
Jako je popularan kod
Americkih turista.

506
00:50:50,791 --> 00:50:53,835
Zašto ne ucinite nesto
ugodno veceras?

507
00:50:54,419 --> 00:50:58,882
Pocastite se s finom vecerom,
dobrom cigarom ili dobrom kurvom?

508
00:51:00,050 --> 00:51:01,593
Radije bih bio sam.

509
00:51:08,183 --> 00:51:10,852
Ostavit cu vas onda samog.

510
00:52:12,164 --> 00:52:13,165
Evo ga.

511
00:52:13,623 --> 00:52:17,127
Privatnost i pogled na prostoriju.
Ako vidite nešto...

512
00:52:17,502 --> 00:52:22,841
...ili nekoga tko vas zanima,
vidjet cu što mogu uciniti.

513
00:52:40,609 --> 00:52:45,322
Ako bih mogla dobiti svoju kavu svako
jutro prije oblacenja bila bih jako sretna.

514
00:52:45,572 --> 00:52:47,574
To bi promijenilo dan.

515
00:52:49,368 --> 00:52:51,036
Bila bih jako sretna.

516
00:52:51,119 --> 00:52:53,121
To bi promijenilo dan.

517
00:52:54,498 --> 00:52:56,500
Onda je to ono što ces i imati.

518
00:52:56,583 --> 00:53:01,046
Kad se oženimo imat ces
sve što poželiš.

519
00:53:02,172 --> 00:53:05,133
Oženimo? Možda bi tvoja žena
imalo štogod reci o tome.

520
00:53:05,759 --> 00:53:07,636
Ovuda, Pukovnice, s'il vous plait.

521
00:53:08,011 --> 00:53:10,514
S'il vous plait i tebi,
ti šašavi šarlatanu.

522
00:53:10,680 --> 00:53:14,726
-Francuz si kao i moja guzica!
-Edwin, zauzdaj jezik.

523
00:53:25,153 --> 00:53:27,322
Mogu li vam pomoci gospodine?

524
00:53:28,323 --> 00:53:30,867
Mislio sam da sam
vidio starog prijatelja.

525
00:53:31,326 --> 00:53:32,285
Pukovnice....

526
00:53:32,369 --> 00:53:33,829
-Pukovnik Worth?
-Da.

527
00:53:33,912 --> 00:53:35,372
Ovuda.

528
00:53:35,497 --> 00:53:36,790
Ne, ne, ne.

529
00:53:37,582 --> 00:53:39,668
Necu mu sad smetati.

530
00:53:40,794 --> 00:53:42,421
Da li je odsjeo u hotelu?

531
00:53:42,462 --> 00:53:46,633
Ne u kuci je u Havani.
Živi u avenida Medios.

532
00:53:47,092 --> 00:53:49,553
Mislim da mu je
zarucnica u hotelu.

533
00:53:50,971 --> 00:53:51,930
Zarucnica?

534
00:53:52,013 --> 00:53:53,849
Da, Miss Castle.

535
00:53:55,642 --> 00:53:57,227
Da, da.

536
00:53:57,978 --> 00:54:00,105
Dobro, hvala.

537
00:54:23,545 --> 00:54:26,131
Draga, ali ja nemam toliko novca.

538
00:54:26,214 --> 00:54:27,799
Ali dragi, imaš.

539
00:54:28,216 --> 00:54:31,511
Tvoji godišnji prihodi su
200 000 dolara, više ili manje.

540
00:54:32,846 --> 00:54:34,347
Kako to znaš?

541
00:54:34,431 --> 00:54:37,309
Zbog toga, što uz povoljne
uvjete možeš ostvariti...

542
00:54:37,350 --> 00:54:42,105
...najmanje 1.5 milion funti (750 000 kila)
šeæera u dobroj sezoni.

543
00:54:42,147 --> 00:54:43,398
Pet centi po funti--

544
00:54:43,482 --> 00:54:47,527
Ne, nemoj. Nemoj me tjerati
da sad govorim o poslu.

545
00:54:51,239 --> 00:54:53,575
Cekao sam na ovo cijelu vecer.

546
00:55:03,043 --> 00:55:05,087
Ne, nemoj gledati.

547
00:55:05,504 --> 00:55:07,339
Budi dobra, moja golubice.

548
00:55:08,006 --> 00:55:09,341
Budi dobra prema starom covjeku.

549
00:55:09,383 --> 00:55:11,093
Ja jesam dobra.

550
00:55:11,259 --> 00:55:13,011
Dobra kao i uvijek.

551
00:55:22,896 --> 00:55:25,065
Možeš li mi, molim te,
otkopcati haljinu?

552
00:55:25,899 --> 00:55:27,818
O, da.

553
00:55:28,068 --> 00:55:29,986
Pruži mi to zadovoljstvo.

554
00:55:35,200 --> 00:55:37,035
To je dosta. Hvala.

555
00:55:37,494 --> 00:55:38,787
Hvala...

556
00:55:39,705 --> 00:55:41,748
...za divnu vecer. Laku noc.

557
00:55:41,832 --> 00:55:43,083
-Ne.
-Da.

558
00:55:43,166 --> 00:55:46,294
Bit cu dobar. Samo cu
sjediti i gledati te.

559
00:55:47,212 --> 00:55:48,547
Vidjet ces...

560
00:55:49,089 --> 00:55:50,757
...sjedit cu...

561
00:55:51,466 --> 00:55:52,718
...i gledati.

562
00:55:52,843 --> 00:55:55,053
Da li je to ono što želiš?

563
00:55:56,471 --> 00:55:59,725
Jako si umoran, a i ja sam.

564
00:56:00,934 --> 00:56:02,477
-Laku noc.
-Ne.

565
00:56:03,645 --> 00:56:06,815
-Ne.
-Laku noc. Da.

566
00:56:06,898 --> 00:56:08,024
Ne.

567
00:56:08,734 --> 00:56:11,903
Mogu li ostati?
Molim te, daj da ostanem.

568
00:56:16,742 --> 00:56:19,202
Draga golubice, ja placem.

569
00:56:19,745 --> 00:56:21,913
Moje srce je puding.

570
00:56:24,583 --> 00:56:25,792
Otici cu.

571
00:56:26,585 --> 00:56:29,087
Ali moj puding je sav slomljen.

572
00:56:30,797 --> 00:56:32,049
Laku noc...

573
00:56:32,883 --> 00:56:34,593
...moja mala golubice.

574
00:56:35,886 --> 00:56:37,220
Laku noc.

575
00:56:38,722 --> 00:56:40,891
"Rastanak je tako slatka tuga."

576
00:57:30,899 --> 00:57:32,901
To sam ja, Julia.

577
00:57:36,655 --> 00:57:38,990
Nisi zaboravila na mene, zar ne?

578
00:57:44,663 --> 00:57:46,123
Tko je Billy?

579
00:57:48,125 --> 00:57:49,793
Samo jedan momak.

580
00:57:51,962 --> 00:57:54,631
Mora da ima preko nekoliko
momaka u tvom životu.

581
00:57:56,216 --> 00:57:57,509
Billy...

582
00:57:58,427 --> 00:57:59,678
...ja...

583
00:58:00,429 --> 00:58:01,763
...Pukovnik.

584
00:58:02,723 --> 00:58:04,391
Da li si se udala
za ikog od njih?

585
00:58:04,599 --> 00:58:07,310
-Ne, samo za tebe.
-Lažljivice.

586
00:58:08,562 --> 00:58:09,938
Lažljivice.

587
00:58:14,443 --> 00:58:15,777
Lažljivice.

588
00:58:23,577 --> 00:58:25,495
Onda, što je?

589
00:58:25,579 --> 00:58:26,913
Što je?

590
00:58:27,914 --> 00:58:29,499
Koji su tvoji planovi sa mnom?

591
00:58:30,333 --> 00:58:31,710
Moji planovi?

592
00:58:33,211 --> 00:58:35,547
Samo sam došao da te ubijem.

593
00:58:43,972 --> 00:58:45,474
Moj bože.

594
00:58:48,977 --> 00:58:50,979
Dobro, ucini to.

595
00:58:59,196 --> 00:59:01,448
Evo. Tu je moje srce.
Nemoj oklijevati.

596
00:59:01,907 --> 00:59:03,950
Tvoj novac je otišao. Ucini to.

597
00:59:04,785 --> 00:59:05,952
Otišao.

598
00:59:07,162 --> 00:59:08,914
Kao i žena koju si ubila?

599
00:59:11,333 --> 00:59:12,334
Šta? Ne.

600
00:59:13,460 --> 00:59:19,091
Bila si s njom na tom brodu!
Vidjeli su vas zajedno!

601
00:59:20,967 --> 00:59:24,012
-Nisam bila sama.
-Rekla ti je sve o meni, zar ne?

602
00:59:24,262 --> 00:59:25,389
Ne!

603
00:59:26,056 --> 00:59:27,557
Rekla sam njemu!

604
00:59:28,100 --> 00:59:32,687
Sutradan mi je rekao da je imala nezgodu
i da zauzmem njeno mjesto, pa jesam.

605
00:59:34,439 --> 00:59:35,774
Drugi covjek?

606
00:59:36,316 --> 00:59:37,651
Suucesnik?

607
00:59:37,734 --> 00:59:39,528
Prijatelj? Ljubavnik?

608
00:59:39,611 --> 00:59:40,946
Suucesnik--

609
00:59:42,531 --> 00:59:46,034
Vidio si nas zajedno,
iza pozornice, na predstavi.

610
00:59:47,119 --> 00:59:49,246
Moj prijatelj, moj suucesnik...

611
00:59:49,663 --> 00:59:52,040
...da, da, moj ljubavnik.

612
00:59:52,499 --> 00:59:55,836
Bio je glumac, kao i ja.
Glumci koji glume uloge.

613
00:59:57,546 --> 01:00:01,299
Rekla sam mu to vece da ne mogu
dalje nastaviti s tim. Da ne mogu--

614
01:00:02,134 --> 01:00:03,468
Zašto ne?

615
01:00:03,719 --> 01:00:04,970
Zato!

616
01:00:05,595 --> 01:00:07,472
Zato što sam....

617
01:00:07,806 --> 01:00:10,308
Prokletstvo. Zato što
sam se zaljubila u mog muža.

618
01:00:10,350 --> 01:00:12,018
Ponovo. Lažljivica.

619
01:00:14,980 --> 01:00:18,650
Mogla sam ga isplatiti!
Mogla sam ga držati podalje!

620
01:00:18,859 --> 01:00:21,820
Ali natjerao si me da pišem
njezinoj sestri i onda je bilo gotovo!

621
01:00:22,154 --> 01:00:23,113
Kurvo!

622
01:00:23,572 --> 01:00:24,698
Lopove!

623
01:00:26,283 --> 01:00:29,036
To je moj život.
To je sve što znam.

624
01:00:29,119 --> 01:00:32,330
Uzela sam novac i dala mu ga.

625
01:00:34,583 --> 01:00:36,585
Onda sam pobjegla.

626
01:00:42,340 --> 01:00:44,009
Šta ima veze?

627
01:00:44,176 --> 01:00:45,844
Šta ima veze?

628
01:00:45,886 --> 01:00:47,179
Gotovo je.

629
01:00:49,806 --> 01:00:51,183
Kurvo!

630
01:00:51,266 --> 01:00:52,809
Lažljivice! Lopove!

631
01:00:52,851 --> 01:00:54,186
Da!

632
01:00:54,352 --> 01:00:56,730
Zar ne vidiš...

633
01:00:57,355 --> 01:01:00,025
...da ne mogu disati bez tebe?

634
01:01:00,108 --> 01:01:01,693
Ne mogu živjeti bez tebe!

635
01:01:01,818 --> 01:01:04,571
Zar ne vidiš to?
Zar ne vidiš koliko te volim?

636
01:01:11,161 --> 01:01:13,372
Žao mi je.

637
01:01:49,408 --> 01:01:51,076
Gdje sam?

638
01:01:55,080 --> 01:01:56,415
Tko si ti?

639
01:02:00,460 --> 01:02:01,586
Stvarno.

640
01:02:02,504 --> 01:02:04,172
Moje ime je Bonny.

641
01:02:05,465 --> 01:02:06,967
Bonny Castle.

642
01:02:09,094 --> 01:02:10,595
Bonny Castle.

643
01:02:14,683 --> 01:02:16,810
Je li to tvoje krsno ime?

644
01:02:17,310 --> 01:02:18,729
Bilo bi...

645
01:02:19,438 --> 01:02:21,064
...da sam kršcanka.

646
01:02:21,857 --> 01:02:23,358
Ali nisam.

647
01:02:25,110 --> 01:02:26,862
Nisam nikad krštena.

648
01:02:27,696 --> 01:02:29,406
Bila sam siroce.

649
01:02:31,950 --> 01:02:33,452
Billy takoðer.

650
01:02:44,296 --> 01:02:47,299
Odrasli smo u sirotištu
izvan St. Louisa.

651
01:02:49,051 --> 01:02:50,761
On mi je dao ime.

652
01:02:51,762 --> 01:02:54,681
Vidio ga je na jednoj
razglednici iz Škotske.

653
01:02:55,140 --> 01:02:59,770
Imala je crtež,
"bonny castle-a", rekao je.

654
01:03:01,313 --> 01:03:04,483
Kad nam je bilo 14,
zajedno smo pobjegli.

655
01:03:05,692 --> 01:03:09,279
Kao brat, sestra, otac, kcer,
muž, žena.

656
01:03:10,197 --> 01:03:12,074
-On je bio moj spas.
-Ne.

657
01:03:16,828 --> 01:03:18,663
Ne želim znati.

658
01:03:20,540 --> 01:03:21,708
Ne sada.

659
01:03:24,336 --> 01:03:28,340
Ti si Julia Russell
iz Wilmington, Delawarea.

660
01:03:30,759 --> 01:03:32,386
Roðena si...

661
01:03:32,928 --> 01:03:35,180
...na dan kad si stupila s broda...

662
01:03:36,223 --> 01:03:38,141
...i postala moja žena.

663
01:03:42,854 --> 01:03:44,356
Ali onda...

664
01:03:44,439 --> 01:03:47,109
...ja nisam Julia Russell, zar ne?

665
01:03:50,195 --> 01:03:51,613
Ja sam jednostavno tvoja žena.

666
01:04:44,791 --> 01:04:46,752
-Tko je to?
-Ne znam.

667
01:04:47,127 --> 01:04:49,254
Edwin je, draga moja.

668
01:04:49,713 --> 01:04:51,715
Jesam li uranio?

669
01:04:52,549 --> 01:04:54,217
Ne žuri se.

670
01:04:54,801 --> 01:04:59,556
Ništa mi ne pruža takav užitak
kao cekati na tebe pred vratima.

671
01:05:00,807 --> 01:05:04,061
Osim, ako me ne želiš
pustiti unutra.

672
01:05:18,617 --> 01:05:21,036
-Pukovnice Worth.
-Bože!

673
01:05:21,203 --> 01:05:24,039
-Mogu li vam pomoci?
-Niste obuceni.

674
01:05:24,664 --> 01:05:26,041
Ne, nisam.

675
01:05:26,625 --> 01:05:29,503
Sad sam zaokupljen s
jednim procesom.

676
01:05:29,586 --> 01:05:33,006
Procesom u kojem je odjeca
samo na smetnji.

677
01:05:33,090 --> 01:05:34,257
Privatnim procesom?

678
01:05:34,466 --> 01:05:35,467
Da gospodine.

679
01:05:35,675 --> 01:05:38,095
Sa Bonny? Privatnim procesom?

680
01:05:38,345 --> 01:05:40,013
Blagi bože!

681
01:05:40,263 --> 01:05:43,433
Baš sam nepristojan. Uðite.

682
01:05:44,434 --> 01:05:45,977
Ne, gospodine. Zar ste ludi?

683
01:05:46,061 --> 01:05:47,729
Lud? Ne.

684
01:05:48,605 --> 01:05:53,110
Samo sam znatiželjan da znam što
tadite pred vratima moje žene.

685
01:05:56,947 --> 01:05:58,365
Vaše žene?

686
01:05:59,658 --> 01:06:01,118
Da li ste rekli, "žene"?

687
01:06:01,618 --> 01:06:03,578
Edwin, budi oprezanl.

688
01:06:03,787 --> 01:06:05,747
Ima strašnu narav.

689
01:06:07,332 --> 01:06:09,376
Oprostite gospodine.

690
01:06:10,210 --> 01:06:11,878
Oprostite.

691
01:06:12,379 --> 01:06:14,214
Ja sam stara budala.

692
01:06:14,715 --> 01:06:16,383
Nisam znao.

693
01:06:18,844 --> 01:06:19,886
Žao mi je.

694
01:06:26,893 --> 01:06:28,895
Dobro vam jutro želim.

695
01:06:29,938 --> 01:06:30,981
Dobro jutro.

696
01:06:39,364 --> 01:06:40,532
Vidiš?

697
01:06:42,325 --> 01:06:43,994
Nemaš prošlosti.

698
01:06:45,245 --> 01:06:47,581
Otišla je. Gotova.

699
01:06:48,248 --> 01:06:49,916
Nestala.

700
01:06:52,419 --> 01:06:54,296
Sad imaš samo mene.

701
01:07:15,233 --> 01:07:17,778
Tu si. Nisi bio
u svojoj sobi.

702
01:07:18,570 --> 01:07:20,989
Imam interesantne vijesti.

703
01:07:21,073 --> 01:07:22,532
I ja isto.

704
01:07:30,082 --> 01:07:31,750
"Pronaðeno tijelo žene."

705
01:07:32,042 --> 01:07:34,544
"Sumnja se na ubistvo."
Kakav je moj Španjolski?

706
01:07:37,756 --> 01:07:39,216
Julia Russell?

707
01:07:40,717 --> 01:07:44,012
Ubodena u vrat s malim nožem,
i bacena preko palube.

708
01:07:44,221 --> 01:07:47,557
Vjerovatno je to ucinio muskarac,
ali lako je mogla biti i žena.

709
01:07:47,766 --> 01:07:50,685
Oštrica noža joj je još
uvijek bila u grlu.

710
01:07:52,771 --> 01:07:54,898
Tako da je tvoja žena...

711
01:07:55,482 --> 01:07:57,901
...i službeno bjegunac.

712
01:07:57,943 --> 01:08:00,779
Ne samo da je mi tražimo,
nego i policija.

713
01:08:02,072 --> 01:08:04,074
Razvedri se. To su dobre vijesti.

714
01:08:04,116 --> 01:08:06,284
Brzo ce je uhvatiti.

715
01:08:07,369 --> 01:08:08,370
Ona...

716
01:08:09,037 --> 01:08:10,706
...nije to napravila.

717
01:08:14,543 --> 01:08:16,712
Vjerujem da ju još voliš.

718
01:08:20,924 --> 01:08:22,050
Naravno.

719
01:08:22,384 --> 01:08:26,555
Kako bi ju mogao toliko mrziti
da ju još ne voliš?

720
01:08:28,974 --> 01:08:32,144
Vjeruj mi prijatelju.
nema takve stvari kao što je ljubav.

721
01:08:32,352 --> 01:08:34,730
Samo pogrešni osjecaji i emocije.

722
01:08:35,063 --> 01:08:37,774
To je bio moj nož. Koristio je moj nož.

723
01:08:38,859 --> 01:08:42,154
-Nisam bila ja. Kunem ti se.
-Vjerujem ti.

724
01:08:42,654 --> 01:08:44,906
Nitko drugi nece vjerovati
da sam nevina.

725
01:08:44,990 --> 01:08:46,324
Slušaj me.

726
01:08:46,408 --> 01:08:48,869
Nitko drugi nije važan. Ne meni.

727
01:09:00,964 --> 01:09:02,632
O cemu misliš?

728
01:09:03,884 --> 01:09:04,885
O tebi.

729
01:09:13,018 --> 01:09:14,978
Dobrodošli u Cardenas.

730
01:09:15,520 --> 01:09:19,441
Ovuda. Ovo je ulaz.
Jako eleganto...

731
01:09:20,025 --> 01:09:22,194
...u jako dobrom dijelu grada.

732
01:09:22,652 --> 01:09:26,239
Uglavnom Amerikanci i
turisti s kontinenta.

733
01:09:27,199 --> 01:09:31,370
Mislim da cete naci sav
namještaj koji vam treba.

734
01:09:31,536 --> 01:09:33,163
Spavacu sobu...

735
01:09:33,455 --> 01:09:36,166
...dnevnu sobu,
jako dobru kuhinju.

736
01:09:39,711 --> 01:09:42,881
Ovdje u Cardenasu,
blizu ste Havani...

737
01:09:43,048 --> 01:09:45,217
...ali jako daleko od nje.

738
01:09:45,884 --> 01:09:50,722
Poznati smo po vodama i
ljekovitoj snazi sunca.

739
01:10:26,091 --> 01:10:27,259
Vargas.

740
01:10:29,261 --> 01:10:30,595
Koja sretna slucajnost.

741
01:10:30,929 --> 01:10:32,764
Da, stvarno.

742
01:10:34,474 --> 01:10:36,476
Što vas dovodi u Cardenas?

743
01:10:36,935 --> 01:10:39,062
Nije odmaranje, uvjeravam vas.

744
01:10:39,938 --> 01:10:41,898
Ne, Naravno da ne.

745
01:10:42,274 --> 01:10:45,610
Ima izvještaj o ženi koja
odgovara oreðenom opisu.

746
01:10:45,944 --> 01:10:48,071
Viðena je kako ulazi
na vlak.

747
01:10:48,363 --> 01:10:51,742
Niste ništa culi ni
vidjeli, zar ne?

748
01:10:52,617 --> 01:10:55,579
Izgubio sam želju za ženama
koje su tog opisa.

749
01:10:56,288 --> 01:10:57,873
Drago mi je to cuti.

750
01:11:00,584 --> 01:11:02,419
Slušajte...

751
01:11:03,712 --> 01:11:05,380
...mogu li vam ponuditi pinales?

752
01:11:05,589 --> 01:11:06,965
Što je to?

753
01:11:07,382 --> 01:11:08,717
Napitak.

754
01:11:10,677 --> 01:11:12,554
Ima kafic dole niz ulicu.

755
01:11:17,225 --> 01:11:18,894
Sunce je toplo.

756
01:11:19,728 --> 01:11:22,481
Tvoje lice je, na primjer,
dosta vlažno.

757
01:11:31,740 --> 01:11:35,744
Sestra je pozitivno identificirala tijelo.

758
01:11:36,078 --> 01:11:38,914
Jako tužno i jako tocno.

759
01:11:39,247 --> 01:11:42,376
Dva madeža visoko na unutrašnjoj
strani bedra...

760
01:11:43,210 --> 01:11:45,462
...i zlatna navlaka na zubu.

761
01:11:45,754 --> 01:11:49,925
I na njenoj lijevoj ruci mali,
kružni ožiljak.

762
01:11:50,759 --> 01:11:52,260
Jako interesantno.

763
01:11:54,513 --> 01:11:57,432
Oprostite.
Moram na WC.

764
01:11:57,682 --> 01:11:59,351
Nema problema.

765
01:12:01,353 --> 01:12:03,021
Napravi što moraš.

766
01:12:35,887 --> 01:12:37,222
Julia?

767
01:12:40,892 --> 01:12:42,894
Doði gore. Mi....

768
01:12:44,896 --> 01:12:46,231
Ah, Luis.

769
01:12:47,691 --> 01:12:49,359
Ja sam razocaran.

770
01:12:52,070 --> 01:12:54,740
I istovremeno pun divljenja.

771
01:12:58,785 --> 01:13:00,120
Gdje je ona?

772
01:13:00,203 --> 01:13:01,538
Tko? Ne.

773
01:13:01,872 --> 01:13:03,623
-Ona nije ovdje.
-Zvao si je po imenu.

774
01:13:03,707 --> 01:13:05,375
Nemaš što tražiti ovdje.

775
01:13:05,709 --> 01:13:09,379
Downs, molim te. Budi pametan i odi.
Odi dok još možeš.

776
01:13:09,713 --> 01:13:10,714
Ona je moja, Luis.

777
01:13:10,839 --> 01:13:12,883
Ostavi je, prije nego
što bude prekasno.

778
01:13:13,550 --> 01:13:15,886
Pomažeš kriminalcu!

779
01:13:16,428 --> 01:13:19,765
I blizu si da i sam
postaneš jedan.

780
01:13:19,848 --> 01:13:21,558
Opameti se.

781
01:13:22,059 --> 01:13:25,062
Vidio si. Nije ovdje.
Sada, molim te.

782
01:13:25,395 --> 01:13:27,773
Ne laži mi, Mr. Vargas.

783
01:13:28,273 --> 01:13:30,108
Mogu je namirisati na tebi.

784
01:13:30,358 --> 01:13:33,862
Njezin parfem se osjeti
na tvojoj odjeci.

785
01:13:34,404 --> 01:13:36,281
Tek si se rastao od nje, zar ne?

786
01:13:36,323 --> 01:13:38,325
To je to. Izlazi!

787
01:13:40,577 --> 01:13:43,830
Da li te je zagrlila?
Prigrlila te, ovako?

788
01:13:43,914 --> 01:13:47,250
Da li je trljala svoj obraz
uz tvoj ovako?

789
01:13:47,584 --> 01:13:49,753
Da li te je poljubila u usta?

790
01:13:49,961 --> 01:13:52,798
Ako te poljubim sad, da li
cu je osjetiti na tebi?

791
01:14:07,646 --> 01:14:09,356
Ovo bi napravio za nju?

792
01:14:11,400 --> 01:14:12,901
Cekaj!

793
01:14:13,026 --> 01:14:14,111
Cekaj.

794
01:14:15,362 --> 01:14:18,365
Govoreci o vragu, a on se pojavi.

795
01:14:26,373 --> 01:14:28,542
Moj bože. Što si napravio?

796
01:14:28,875 --> 01:14:30,544
Što si napravio?

797
01:14:30,836 --> 01:14:32,170
To je on.

798
01:14:33,004 --> 01:14:34,840
To je detektiv.

799
01:14:36,383 --> 01:14:38,051
Došao je po tebe.

800
01:14:47,102 --> 01:14:49,187
Što to radiš? Ne diraj ga.

801
01:14:49,271 --> 01:14:50,981
Ne diraj ga!

802
01:14:58,447 --> 01:15:01,074
-Da li je došao sam?
-Da.

803
01:15:01,408 --> 01:15:03,076
Nitko ga nije vidio kako dolazi?

804
01:15:05,245 --> 01:15:06,747
Ne znam.

805
01:15:07,080 --> 01:15:09,082
Isuse, Julia.

806
01:15:09,916 --> 01:15:11,376
Ubio sam covjeka.

807
01:15:11,918 --> 01:15:14,212
Moras otici na željeznicku stanicu.

808
01:15:14,421 --> 01:15:17,966
Kupi dvije karte za vlak,
nije bitno za kud.

809
01:15:19,926 --> 01:15:23,680
Kontaktirat cu agenta za nekretnine
i reci mu da smo se predomislili...

810
01:15:23,805 --> 01:15:26,224
...i da je bilo hitno.

811
01:15:28,143 --> 01:15:29,478
Julia.

812
01:15:31,313 --> 01:15:32,814
Da, što?

813
01:15:34,483 --> 01:15:36,401
Upravo sam ubio covjeka.

814
01:15:38,320 --> 01:15:40,155
A ja sam kupila šešir.

815
01:15:43,658 --> 01:15:48,663
Ali ne raspravljam o tome. Ne ponavljam
stalno "kupila sam šešir".

816
01:15:48,997 --> 01:15:51,833
"Kupila sam šešir." Nije važno.

817
01:15:53,502 --> 01:15:55,837
Ucinjeno je. Pomozi mi.

818
01:15:57,589 --> 01:15:58,757
Bože.

819
01:16:10,435 --> 01:16:13,021
-Bit ce dobro.
-Odnijet cu ga dole.

820
01:16:13,939 --> 01:16:16,608
Ne, odi na stanicu prije
nego što se zatvori.

821
01:16:18,151 --> 01:16:20,112
Doði. Obuci ovo.

822
01:16:20,195 --> 01:16:21,488
Da, požurit cu.

823
01:16:21,571 --> 01:16:23,198
Ne. Nemoj žuriti.

824
01:16:23,448 --> 01:16:26,868
Hodaj polako, uživaj u šetnji
i nitko te nece primjetiti.

825
01:16:27,452 --> 01:16:29,246
-Razumiješ?
-Da.

826
01:17:03,488 --> 01:17:04,823
Billy.

827
01:17:06,408 --> 01:17:07,993
Konacno si dobio što si zaslužio.

828
01:17:22,007 --> 01:17:24,342
-Isuse!
-Zar ti nije drago što me vidiš?

829
01:17:24,384 --> 01:17:26,970
Zar ti nije drago da ponovno
vidiš starog Detektiva Downsa?

830
01:17:27,179 --> 01:17:28,221
Zar bi trebalo biti?

831
01:17:28,472 --> 01:17:31,600
Dobio sam jako dobre kritike
igrajuci ovu ulogu u Chicagu.

832
01:17:31,767 --> 01:17:33,185
Zar se ne sjecas?

833
01:17:33,268 --> 01:17:35,103
Pusti me, Billy.

834
01:17:35,312 --> 01:17:37,647
Mislila si da sam ...

835
01:17:38,482 --> 01:17:40,150
...stvarno mrtav...

836
01:17:41,693 --> 01:17:42,986
...nisi li?

837
01:17:53,747 --> 01:17:56,333
Zar si mislila da su pravi
meci u tom pištolju?

838
01:17:56,875 --> 01:18:00,253
Mislila si da su pravi one
noci kad te je došao ubiti?

839
01:18:01,421 --> 01:18:05,926
Nisam mogao riskirati da te ubije,
ne prije nego što te ja uhvatim.

840
01:18:07,094 --> 01:18:09,054
-Pusti me, Billy.
-Nikad.

841
01:18:09,262 --> 01:18:11,723
-Ne dok se ne vratiš u igru.
-Koju igru?

842
01:18:11,848 --> 01:18:13,809
Našu igru, draga.

843
01:18:13,892 --> 01:18:15,227
Nema nikave igre.

844
01:18:15,435 --> 01:18:17,229
Da, jasno to vidim.

845
01:18:17,437 --> 01:18:19,106
Ne, ne.

846
01:18:19,940 --> 01:18:21,441
Što vidiš?

847
01:18:23,610 --> 01:18:27,114
Vidim kako trci po novac.
Vidim kako ti to sreðuješ.

848
01:18:27,572 --> 01:18:29,825
Vidim kako cini jedinu stvar
koju može.

849
01:18:29,908 --> 01:18:33,537
Vidim kako ide u Santiago,
prodajuci svoj dio kompanije.

850
01:18:33,620 --> 01:18:35,956
Vidim kako se vraca s novcem.

851
01:18:36,123 --> 01:18:37,749
Vidim nas...

852
01:18:37,958 --> 01:18:39,710
...kako završavamo ono
što smo poceli.

853
01:18:40,293 --> 01:18:41,712
Ti i ja zajedno.

854
01:18:41,837 --> 01:18:44,506
Napravit cemo te
bogatom udovicom.

855
01:18:50,470 --> 01:18:53,932
On vrijedi puno više nego što
smo izvukli od njega prvi put.

856
01:18:53,974 --> 01:18:57,436
I tako je laka meta kad
ti je toliko odan.

857
01:18:57,894 --> 01:19:02,566
Spojeni ste zajedno raznim
zlocinima i...

858
01:19:02,941 --> 01:19:04,443
...nepodopštinama.

859
01:19:05,444 --> 01:19:07,571
-Pusti me.
-Moli.

860
01:19:07,946 --> 01:19:09,781
-Molim te, pusti me!
-Moli.

861
01:19:12,784 --> 01:19:16,121
Skakljuca mi pimpek kad moliš.

862
01:19:17,622 --> 01:19:20,083
Rekao je da me voli.

863
01:19:23,128 --> 01:19:24,963
Nitko te ne voli, Bonny.

864
01:19:25,005 --> 01:19:26,590
Nitko to ne može.

865
01:19:26,965 --> 01:19:28,425
Osim mene.

866
01:19:30,302 --> 01:19:31,636
On može.

867
01:19:32,012 --> 01:19:33,430
Mislim da može.

868
01:19:33,555 --> 01:19:36,558
Ne dovoljno da živi
život kao bjegunac.

869
01:19:38,310 --> 01:19:40,645
Stražnje ulicice, jeftini hoteli....

870
01:19:40,854 --> 01:19:42,230
Nece biti tako.

871
01:19:42,314 --> 01:19:44,066
Nego kako?
Sretni do kraja života?

872
01:19:44,608 --> 01:19:47,486
Lijep, uvaženi par,
koji živi u glavnoj ulici?

873
01:19:47,569 --> 01:19:50,614
Nedjeljni ruckovi,
šetnje u parku s djecicom?

874
01:19:51,823 --> 01:19:54,159
Isuse, što ti je to ucinio?

875
01:19:54,826 --> 01:19:56,870
Što ti misliš tko si?

876
01:19:57,329 --> 01:19:59,414
Što on misli tko si ti?

877
01:20:00,665 --> 01:20:02,626
Ti si kurva, Bonny.

878
01:20:02,918 --> 01:20:05,921
Ako muškarac stavi ruku na tebe
odmah si vlažna.

879
01:20:07,923 --> 01:20:09,591
Istina ili ne?

880
01:20:13,512 --> 01:20:15,514
Roðena si sama i umrijet ces sama.

881
01:20:15,764 --> 01:20:18,433
Prije nego kasnije ako
te policija uhvati.

882
01:20:21,520 --> 01:20:23,188
Ne bi mi to ucinio.

883
01:20:23,438 --> 01:20:26,775
Bio sam ti prvi, Bonny.
Tvoj prvi.

884
01:20:27,609 --> 01:20:29,486
I bit cu...

885
01:20:29,653 --> 01:20:31,154
...tvoj zadnji.

886
01:20:32,697 --> 01:20:34,533
Na ovaj ili onaj nacin.

887
01:20:37,244 --> 01:20:39,746
Nema buducnosti s njim, draga.

888
01:20:40,580 --> 01:20:42,416
Suoci se s istinom.

889
01:20:43,250 --> 01:20:45,419
Ne možeš živjeti njegov život.

890
01:20:45,919 --> 01:20:47,379
A on sigurno...

891
01:20:47,796 --> 01:20:49,548
...ne može živjeti tvoj.

892
01:20:51,091 --> 01:20:52,592
Pusti ga.

893
01:20:55,554 --> 01:20:56,680
Ne.

894
01:20:56,888 --> 01:20:58,140
Pusti ga.

895
01:20:59,891 --> 01:21:01,351
Pusti ga.

896
01:21:50,442 --> 01:21:52,069
Bila sam tako gladna.

897
01:21:55,197 --> 01:21:58,450
Što s njim?
Moramo se riješiti tijela.

898
01:21:58,867 --> 01:22:00,369
Vec je obavljeno.

899
01:22:01,661 --> 01:22:02,871
Obavljeno je?

900
01:22:05,791 --> 01:22:07,417
Misliš, sama si to obavila?

901
01:22:08,293 --> 01:22:12,881
I spakirala sam nam stvari.
Ostavila sam jedno odijelo na krevetu, za vlak.

902
01:22:13,715 --> 01:22:15,217
Imaš karte?

903
01:22:16,176 --> 01:22:18,136
-Karte? Da.
-Odlicno.

904
01:22:18,345 --> 01:22:20,263
Ici cemo sutra ujutro.

905
01:22:20,347 --> 01:22:22,474
Natrag u Havanu. 7:00.

906
01:22:24,976 --> 01:22:26,686
Koja avantura.

907
01:22:29,815 --> 01:22:31,274
Doði u krevet.

908
01:22:32,526 --> 01:22:34,403
Mora da si izmoren.

909
01:22:34,736 --> 01:22:35,779
Znam da ja jesam.

910
01:22:35,862 --> 01:22:38,198
Cekaj, cekaj, cekaj.

911
01:22:38,865 --> 01:22:41,201
Zar nemaš nimalo savjesti?

912
01:22:41,702 --> 01:22:43,036
Mislim....

913
01:22:44,371 --> 01:22:45,706
Naravno da imam.

914
01:22:46,039 --> 01:22:49,376
Ali vidiš, ne dopuštam da me ovlada.

915
01:22:50,502 --> 01:22:53,547
To je samo nešto što se dogodilo.
Moralo se napraviti.

916
01:22:54,381 --> 01:22:56,967
A kada nešto moraš napraviti,
napraviš, zar ne?

917
01:22:57,050 --> 01:23:01,388
Za nas.
Kratak, ali uzbudljiv život.

918
01:23:06,351 --> 01:23:07,310
Laku noc.

919
01:23:12,524 --> 01:23:14,192
Slušaj njezin govor.

920
01:23:14,693 --> 01:23:17,654
Slušaj rijeci koje izlaze
iz njenih usta.

921
01:23:17,738 --> 01:23:19,239
Misliš Bonny?

922
01:23:20,031 --> 01:23:21,491
Da, Bonny.

923
01:23:24,244 --> 01:23:26,747
Zar nemaš kontrolu nad njom?

924
01:23:28,457 --> 01:23:30,876
Nitko nema kontrolu nad njom.

925
01:23:31,585 --> 01:23:33,086
Nitko nije imao.

926
01:23:36,048 --> 01:23:38,884
Nitko, osim Billya.

927
01:23:40,218 --> 01:23:42,554
I htio je ostatak novca.

928
01:23:46,058 --> 01:23:49,019
Našli su kucu u
siromašnom dijelu grada.

929
01:23:49,394 --> 01:23:53,023
Bonny je rekla da ce proci nezapaženo
tamo, i bila je u pravu.

930
01:23:53,982 --> 01:23:56,985
Puno stvari je prošlo nezapaženo
u toj kuci.

931
01:23:59,404 --> 01:24:01,823
Sve što je trebala napraviti
je dovesti Luisa u Santiago...

932
01:24:03,325 --> 01:24:05,452
...i sve bi bilo gotovo.

933
01:24:11,833 --> 01:24:14,169
Ne, ne razumiješ.

934
01:24:15,504 --> 01:24:18,673
-Ostali smo bez novaca?
-Da, otici cu sutra u Santiago.

935
01:24:18,924 --> 01:24:21,343
Otici cu ujutro prvim vlakom.

936
01:24:23,845 --> 01:24:25,555
Što ceš tamo?

937
01:24:25,680 --> 01:24:27,849
Treba nam novaca, zar ne?

938
01:24:30,018 --> 01:24:31,853
Kako god kažeš.

939
01:24:48,036 --> 01:24:50,455
Ne želim da ideš u Santiago.

940
01:24:52,416 --> 01:24:53,458
Moram ici.

941
01:24:53,542 --> 01:24:55,043
Ne želim da ideš.

942
01:24:55,377 --> 01:24:56,920
Nemam izbora.

943
01:24:58,046 --> 01:24:59,881
Imaš. Imaš izbora.

944
01:25:01,466 --> 01:25:02,843
Još jednom.

945
01:25:03,093 --> 01:25:05,721
-Kad mi ruka dotakne grudi....
-Srce.

946
01:25:06,054 --> 01:25:07,973
-Moja lijeva naušnica.
-Karo.

947
01:25:08,098 --> 01:25:09,850
-Moja desna naušnica.
-Tref.

948
01:25:10,267 --> 01:25:11,768
-Moje grlo.
-Pik.

949
01:25:12,060 --> 01:25:14,688
-Mali prst na lijevoj ruci.
-Jedan.

950
01:25:14,813 --> 01:25:16,815
-Mali prst na desnoj ruci.
-Deset.

951
01:25:17,441 --> 01:25:19,693
Kada ovo napravim, znaci
da nemam ništa.

952
01:25:19,776 --> 01:25:20,944
Dobro.

953
01:25:23,238 --> 01:25:24,990
-Kralj, kraljica, decko.
-Da.

954
01:25:26,450 --> 01:25:27,951
Da.

955
01:25:29,661 --> 01:25:30,829
Ti si prirodan.

956
01:25:31,163 --> 01:25:33,123
-Slušaj--
-To je nacin.

957
01:25:33,248 --> 01:25:35,250
To je jedini nacin.
To je naš nacin.

958
01:25:35,751 --> 01:25:38,420
To smo ti i ja, zajedno.

959
01:25:40,589 --> 01:25:41,923
Molim te.

960
01:25:45,177 --> 01:25:46,470
Sad...

961
01:25:47,012 --> 01:25:49,848
...reci mi što imam.

962
01:26:03,361 --> 01:26:05,322
Želiš li još viskija?

963
01:26:08,075 --> 01:26:09,242
Prejako za mene.

964
01:26:11,203 --> 01:26:13,372
Da. Zašto ne?

965
01:26:14,539 --> 01:26:17,209
Zašto da ne? U redu.

966
01:26:18,877 --> 01:26:20,170
Pobjeðuje ponovo.

967
01:26:20,712 --> 01:26:22,547
Žao mi je, gospodo.

968
01:26:23,048 --> 01:26:24,549
Još šampanjca.

969
01:26:29,554 --> 01:26:32,057
Da li bi dami smetalo
ako skinem sako?

970
01:26:32,265 --> 01:26:34,267
Ne, samo naprijed.

971
01:26:34,643 --> 01:26:36,978
Možete zaboraviti da
sam uopce ovdje.

972
01:26:37,187 --> 01:26:38,688
Lakše reci nego uciniti.

973
01:26:44,027 --> 01:26:45,862
Mogu li vam donijeti
još jedno pice?

974
01:27:19,229 --> 01:27:21,773
Možete li reci dami da se makne?

975
01:27:24,609 --> 01:27:25,986
Kako to mislite?

976
01:27:26,069 --> 01:27:27,446
Zar vam se mora reci?

977
01:27:28,655 --> 01:27:31,992
Maknite ruke s moje žene.
Molim vas, gospodine.

978
01:27:33,410 --> 01:27:34,494
Rado.

979
01:27:36,121 --> 01:27:39,499
Jedina stvar niža od covjeka
koji vara na kartama...

980
01:27:39,583 --> 01:27:43,003
...je covjek koji koristi ženu
da vara umjesto njega.

981
01:28:17,371 --> 01:28:18,705
Julia?

982
01:28:26,046 --> 01:28:27,381
Dakle, draga moja...

983
01:28:29,549 --> 01:28:32,719
...da vidimo koje još trikove
možda znate.

984
01:29:00,706 --> 01:29:02,416
Da li ste u redu?

985
01:29:02,874 --> 01:29:04,000
Da.

986
01:29:05,043 --> 01:29:06,169
Da li....

987
01:29:06,878 --> 01:29:09,214
Da li da pozovem nekoga?

988
01:29:13,552 --> 01:29:15,178
Tako ste dobri.

989
01:29:17,723 --> 01:29:21,017
Tako ste mladi i nevini
i dobri.

990
01:29:23,854 --> 01:29:25,021
Ne.

991
01:29:25,981 --> 01:29:27,524
Nitko nije nevin.

992
01:29:33,739 --> 01:29:35,866
Vi takoðer imate pricu.

993
01:29:37,909 --> 01:29:39,536
Hocete mi ju reci...

994
01:29:41,246 --> 01:29:42,873
...ako bude bilo vremena?

995
01:29:45,083 --> 01:29:47,044
Nemam pricu.

996
01:29:48,420 --> 01:29:50,005
Ne kao vašu.

997
01:29:50,922 --> 01:29:53,550
To je bila Bonnyna prica.

998
01:29:55,594 --> 01:29:57,429
I pogledajte što je ucinila.

999
01:30:00,348 --> 01:30:02,559
Nije mogao živjeti
u njezinom svijetu.

1000
01:30:03,185 --> 01:30:05,520
A ona se nije mogla
uklopiti u njegov.

1001
01:30:06,188 --> 01:30:08,523
Nikad mu nije mogla
biti dostojna.

1002
01:30:11,318 --> 01:30:13,278
Morala ga je pustiti.

1003
01:30:14,863 --> 01:30:16,531
Morala je biti Bonny.

1004
01:30:17,365 --> 01:30:20,369
Cisto, cvrsto i jednostavno.

1005
01:30:23,705 --> 01:30:25,707
Luis ce otici u Santiago.

1006
01:30:27,459 --> 01:30:29,044
Ona ce prezivjeti.

1007
01:30:59,658 --> 01:31:01,118
Dragi Alan:

1008
01:31:01,660 --> 01:31:03,328
Cestitam.

1009
01:31:03,954 --> 01:31:08,959
Upravo si kupio moj udio u
Vargas-Jordan Coffee Export House.

1010
01:31:10,001 --> 01:31:13,672
Cijena na koju sam pristao je jednaka
sumi koja je bila u sefu...

1011
01:31:14,005 --> 01:31:18,343
...Koja je vjerujem jako
u tvoju korist. Žao mi je.

1012
01:31:18,677 --> 01:31:20,220
Luis! Cekaj!

1013
01:31:20,345 --> 01:31:23,473
Žao mi je što nisam mogao ostati
da prodiskutiram o tome s tobom.

1014
01:31:24,516 --> 01:31:28,520
Ali, kao što znaš, sad
sam bjegunac od pravde.

1015
01:31:28,854 --> 01:31:31,189
Više od toga ti ne mogu reci.

1016
01:31:31,523 --> 01:31:33,525
O cemu to pricas?

1017
01:31:33,817 --> 01:31:34,818
Ubistvo.

1018
01:31:36,695 --> 01:31:38,321
Ubio sam.

1019
01:31:39,030 --> 01:31:40,699
-Ne.
-Da.

1020
01:31:41,032 --> 01:31:42,534
Ucinio sam to zbog nje.

1021
01:31:43,869 --> 01:31:45,537
A istina je...

1022
01:31:46,371 --> 01:31:47,998
...da bi to ponovo ucinio.

1023
01:31:52,044 --> 01:31:53,712
Puno ti srece želim.

1024
01:31:54,046 --> 01:31:56,548
Hvala ti što si mi jednom
bio prijatelj.

1025
01:31:59,176 --> 01:32:00,510
Idi.

1026
01:32:07,100 --> 01:32:08,477
Neka ti bog pomogne.

1027
01:34:06,832 --> 01:34:08,458
Hoceš li mi upaliti cigaru?

1028
01:34:11,711 --> 01:34:13,630
Napravit cu nam kavu.

1029
01:34:21,680 --> 01:34:22,931
Prokletstvo!

1030
01:34:23,014 --> 01:34:24,975
-Što se dogodilo?
-Tamo je štakor.

1031
01:34:25,142 --> 01:34:28,186
-Štakor?
-Štakor. Pretcao mi je preko noge.

1032
01:34:29,729 --> 01:34:31,064
Vidiš ga?

1033
01:34:31,773 --> 01:34:32,774
Ne.

1034
01:34:38,196 --> 01:34:39,990
-Nisam ga vidio.
-Ne?

1035
01:34:40,031 --> 01:34:41,366
Što to radiš?

1036
01:34:41,575 --> 01:34:43,243
Idem kod ljekarnika.

1037
01:34:43,577 --> 01:34:45,370
-U ovo vrijeme?
-Da.

1038
01:34:45,620 --> 01:34:48,790
-Sad je 9.00. Zatvoreno je.
-Znam da se ne otvara do 10:00.

1039
01:34:48,874 --> 01:34:51,501
-Što to radiš? Cekaj.
-Necu dugo.

1040
01:36:48,243 --> 01:36:51,163
Ne možeš ga spasiti, ako je to
ono o cemu razmišljaš.

1041
01:36:51,204 --> 01:36:53,874
Zašto ne? Zašto ne možemo
samo otici?

1042
01:36:54,916 --> 01:36:57,085
Imam dvije karte za vlak za nas.

1043
01:36:57,627 --> 01:36:59,755
Nocas, ponoc. Imamo novac.

1044
01:37:00,338 --> 01:37:01,047
Ostavi ga.

1045
01:37:01,131 --> 01:37:04,968
Bonny, to ti ne pristaje,
ovakva samilost.

1046
01:37:06,470 --> 01:37:10,307
Kako da ti vjerujem?
Uvijek ce biti netko izmeðu nas.

1047
01:37:10,557 --> 01:37:12,225
Zašto ga treba ozlijediti?

1048
01:37:12,476 --> 01:37:14,478
On je dio tebe koji mora umrijeti.

1049
01:37:14,728 --> 01:37:18,190
Moraš to ubiti, ili ti obecavam
da ce to ubiti tebe.

1050
01:37:19,483 --> 01:37:21,234
Što to radiš? Billy?

1051
01:37:21,318 --> 01:37:24,738
Vracam se s tobom da
završim taj posao.

1052
01:37:24,821 --> 01:37:28,158
-Navuci ceš policiju na nas.
-Onda napravi kako ti se kaže.

1053
01:37:28,200 --> 01:37:29,493
Napravi sad.

1054
01:37:40,337 --> 01:37:41,963
-Reci.
-Billy--

1055
01:37:42,047 --> 01:37:44,382
Reci da si moja. Moja. Reci.

1056
01:37:44,424 --> 01:37:45,759
Da, što?

1057
01:37:46,051 --> 01:37:47,886
Da, tvoja sam.

1058
01:38:30,929 --> 01:38:32,556
Preplašio si me.

1059
01:38:33,974 --> 01:38:35,642
Trebalo ti je dugo.

1060
01:38:39,771 --> 01:38:41,606
Što to radiš u mraku?

1061
01:38:41,815 --> 01:38:43,150
Razmišljam.

1062
01:38:43,775 --> 01:38:45,360
O èemu?

1063
01:38:47,446 --> 01:38:51,283
Razmišljam kako ce moj život biti
gotov ako te ikada izgubim.

1064
01:38:52,951 --> 01:38:55,287
Ništa mi nece ostati.

1065
01:38:56,538 --> 01:38:58,206
Osim smrti.

1066
01:39:01,960 --> 01:39:03,587
Ne govori trako.

1067
01:39:05,464 --> 01:39:07,382
Jesi li našla što si tražila?

1068
01:39:07,466 --> 01:39:09,009
Jesam.

1069
01:39:09,760 --> 01:39:11,887
Morala sam ici na drugi kraj grada.

1070
01:39:16,558 --> 01:39:18,393
Idem se presvuci.

1071
01:39:30,655 --> 01:39:34,076
Operi ruke i idi u krevet.
Donijet cu kavu.

1072
01:40:01,603 --> 01:40:03,021
Evo ga.

1073
01:40:18,453 --> 01:40:20,288
Što misliš, kako umiru?

1074
01:40:23,959 --> 01:40:25,460
Od otrova?

1075
01:40:26,795 --> 01:40:28,130
Ne znam.

1076
01:40:33,176 --> 01:40:35,178
Da li im treba dugo?

1077
01:40:37,889 --> 01:40:40,559
Mislim da ovisi o tome
koliko im daš.

1078
01:40:40,976 --> 01:40:42,644
U pravu si.

1079
01:40:45,647 --> 01:40:46,982
Da li je bolno?

1080
01:40:47,649 --> 01:40:50,068
Stvarno ne želim o tome razmišljati.

1081
01:40:52,738 --> 01:40:54,573
Ne, naravno da ne.

1082
01:40:55,031 --> 01:40:59,536
Ne želimo da nas obuzme savjest,
zar ne?

1083
01:41:01,872 --> 01:41:04,791
To je nešto što treba obaviti.

1084
01:41:05,709 --> 01:41:07,961
A kad nešto treba obaviti...

1085
01:41:09,045 --> 01:41:10,547
...obaviš to.

1086
01:41:11,047 --> 01:41:12,632
Da li je tvoja kava prevruca?

1087
01:41:13,216 --> 01:41:14,551
Vidio sam ga.

1088
01:41:17,971 --> 01:41:19,306
Koga?

1089
01:41:21,391 --> 01:41:22,893
Pratio sam te.

1090
01:41:23,727 --> 01:41:25,103
Koga si vidio? Gdje?

1091
01:41:26,396 --> 01:41:27,731
Julia.

1092
01:41:29,399 --> 01:41:31,693
Hocemo li se igrati...

1093
01:41:31,777 --> 01:41:34,071
...ili govoriti istinu?

1094
01:41:37,074 --> 01:41:38,575
The truth is best.

1095
01:41:38,909 --> 01:41:40,410
U redu onda.

1096
01:41:42,496 --> 01:41:43,497
Da li je on ovdje?

1097
01:41:45,499 --> 01:41:46,666
Da.

1098
01:41:48,126 --> 01:41:49,252
Gdje?

1099
01:41:50,003 --> 01:41:52,839
Vani, ceka.
Da ugasim svjetla.

1100
01:41:53,507 --> 01:41:55,008
Kad sam mrtav?

1101
01:41:57,177 --> 01:41:58,345
Da.

1102
01:42:02,808 --> 01:42:05,018
Doveo sam ga to tebe u Havani,
nisam li?

1103
01:42:06,144 --> 01:42:07,104
Da.

1104
01:42:08,522 --> 01:42:10,482
Kako je znao da te necu ubiti?

1105
01:42:12,359 --> 01:42:15,028
Stavio je slijepe metke
u pištolj.

1106
01:42:24,371 --> 01:42:25,705
Kao u predstavi.

1107
01:42:27,541 --> 01:42:28,875
Sve.

1108
01:42:31,211 --> 01:42:32,546
Laži.

1109
01:42:33,880 --> 01:42:35,841
Od prvog trenutka
kad sam te sreo.

1110
01:42:36,883 --> 01:42:38,718
Ne sve, ne.

1111
01:42:39,052 --> 01:42:42,305
Da li mi se smijete iza leða,
vas dvoje?

1112
01:42:44,850 --> 01:42:47,978
Da li mi se smijete
kako glup sam bio?

1113
01:42:50,188 --> 01:42:51,523
Kako slijep?

1114
01:42:53,442 --> 01:42:54,651
Ne.

1115
01:42:55,986 --> 01:42:58,321
Smij se sad kad ti ovo kažem.

1116
01:43:00,323 --> 01:43:01,658
Volio sam te, Julia.

1117
01:43:02,409 --> 01:43:04,745
Julia nije ovdje. Julia je mrtva.

1118
01:43:05,829 --> 01:43:10,000
Smij se kad ti kažem
da te još uvijek volim.

1119
01:43:10,542 --> 01:43:11,543
Ne.

1120
01:43:12,335 --> 01:43:13,795
Ne, ne mene.

1121
01:43:14,045 --> 01:43:15,380
Ti ne voliš mene.

1122
01:43:15,672 --> 01:43:17,007
Da.

1123
01:43:18,175 --> 01:43:20,010
Da, tebe.

1124
01:43:21,344 --> 01:43:24,014
Ne Juliu Russell. Ne...

1125
01:43:25,348 --> 01:43:26,850
...Bonny Castle.

1126
01:43:28,101 --> 01:43:29,102
Tebe.

1127
01:43:30,520 --> 01:43:32,355
Volim te takvu kakva jesi.

1128
01:43:32,898 --> 01:43:34,483
Zato što te znam.

1129
01:43:37,027 --> 01:43:38,361
Takvu kakva jesi.

1130
01:43:40,363 --> 01:43:42,032
Dobru i lošu.

1131
01:43:42,532 --> 01:43:44,284
Bolju i lošiju.

1132
01:43:47,788 --> 01:43:50,957
Vec sam ti to prije rekao,
ali nisi mi vjerovala.

1133
01:43:53,210 --> 01:43:54,878
Veceras budeš.

1134
01:43:57,130 --> 01:43:58,465
Za nas.

1135
01:44:00,926 --> 01:44:03,553
Za kratak i uzbudljiv život.

1136
01:44:04,304 --> 01:44:05,972
Ne radi to.

1137
01:44:07,140 --> 01:44:08,725
Nitko drugi.

1138
01:44:13,647 --> 01:44:15,816
Nitko drugi osim tebe.

1139
01:44:20,320 --> 01:44:21,696
Od pocetka do kraja.

1140
01:44:24,491 --> 01:44:26,076
Starta do finiša.

1141
01:44:30,372 --> 01:44:33,208
Nemoj se promijeniti, Julia.
Nemoj se nikad promijeniti.

1142
01:45:02,487 --> 01:45:04,322
Drži se.

1143
01:45:58,835 --> 01:46:00,170
Idemo.

1144
01:46:53,515 --> 01:46:55,058
Razocarala si me, Bonny.

1145
01:47:00,230 --> 01:47:01,773
Što ti misliš?

1146
01:47:01,857 --> 01:47:04,067
Misliš li da su to pravi meci?

1147
01:47:23,170 --> 01:47:25,297
-Govoriš li ti Engleski?
-Da!

1148
01:47:25,839 --> 01:47:27,257
Treba mu doktor.

1149
01:47:27,382 --> 01:47:28,717
A njemu?

1150
01:47:41,354 --> 01:47:43,690
On je mrtav. Ovome treba doktor.

1151
01:47:43,774 --> 01:47:46,693
U redu. Ja zovem policiju.

1152
01:47:54,117 --> 01:47:56,620
Ostani.

1153
01:47:56,703 --> 01:47:59,539
Volim te.

1154
01:48:00,040 --> 01:48:03,043
Volim te. Da li me cuješ?

1155
01:48:04,127 --> 01:48:09,049
-Reci. Reci ponovo.
-Volim te. Volim te.

1156
01:48:09,132 --> 01:48:11,301
Volim te, Luis.

1157
01:48:17,682 --> 01:48:19,851
Drži se! Drži se!

1158
01:48:21,853 --> 01:48:23,939
Ne odlazi! Ostani!

1159
01:48:24,189 --> 01:48:26,149
Molim te, drži se.

1160
01:48:45,210 --> 01:48:50,048
I ovdje prica završava,
bar za mene.

1161
01:48:52,551 --> 01:48:54,719
Cak i ako je sad živ...

1162
01:48:55,387 --> 01:48:57,222
...kako da doðem do njega?

1163
01:49:03,061 --> 01:49:04,896
Da li vjerujete u oprost?

1164
01:49:07,315 --> 01:49:08,358
Da.

1165
01:49:08,400 --> 01:49:10,944
I iskupljenje za ljudsku dušu?

1166
01:49:20,078 --> 01:49:21,204
Da.

1167
01:49:21,747 --> 01:49:23,749
Cak i za nekoga kao ja?

1168
01:49:26,251 --> 01:49:27,377
Da.

1169
01:49:28,712 --> 01:49:30,213
Vjerujem.

1170
01:49:31,715 --> 01:49:34,426
Vidjet cu ga na nebu, zar ne?

1171
01:49:42,476 --> 01:49:43,727
Da.

1172
01:49:47,439 --> 01:49:49,274
Hocete li mi dodati moj šal?

1173
01:49:49,357 --> 01:49:50,400
Da, naravno.

1174
01:49:57,741 --> 01:50:00,077
Sad se molite sa mnom.

1175
01:50:00,702 --> 01:50:01,703
Da.

1176
01:50:05,540 --> 01:50:08,210
Nosila sam ovo na mom vjencanju.

1177
01:50:09,503 --> 01:50:12,506
Ali moje srce nije tada bilo za to.

1178
01:51:03,849 --> 01:51:06,518
Žao mi je gospoðo. Vrijeme je.

1179
01:51:17,946 --> 01:51:19,448
Mogu li?

1180
01:51:22,576 --> 01:51:24,244
Što do vraga!

1181
01:51:24,536 --> 01:51:27,289
-To je svecenik.
-Ali on je otišao prije sat vremena.

1182
01:51:27,497 --> 01:51:28,707
Vidio sam ga.

1183
01:51:29,291 --> 01:51:31,626
Straža!

1184
01:52:08,080 --> 01:52:13,085
Moram priznati da je užitak biti u
